iquor%20policy%20case%20which%20central%20agencies%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20and%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20are%20investigating.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESisodia%20is%20a%20leader%20of%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%2C%20which%20is%20in%20opposition%20to%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party.%20He%20is%20one%20of%20several%20high%20profile%20party%20leaders%20to%20have%20been%20held%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20liquor%20policy%20case%2C%20in%20what%20opposition%20parties%20including%20the%20AAP%20have%20referred%20to%20as%20an%20act%20of%20political%20vendetta.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fsupreme-court-manish-sisodia-aap-bail-delhi-excise-policy-241147%5C%22%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported%20that%20a%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20and%20S.V.N.%20Bhatti%20said%20that%20while%20there%20were%20%E2%80%9Ccertain%20aspects%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20case%20which%20the%20court%20held%20as%20doubtful%2C%20the%20one%20which%20concerns%20the%20transfer%20of%20Rs%20338%20crores%20is%20%E2%80%9Ctentatively%20established.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLegal%20questions%20have%20been%20answered%20in%20a%20limited%20way.%20In%20the%20analysis%2C%20there%20are%20certain%20aspects%2C%20which%20we%20said%20are%20doubtful.%20But%20one%20aspect%2C%20with%20regard%20to%20transfer%20of%20money%2C%20Rs%20338%20crores%2C%20is%20tentatively%20established.%20We%20have%20therefore%20dismissed%20the%20application%20for%20bail%2C%E2%80%9D%20Justice%20Khanna%20was%20quoted%20as%20having%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20various%20points%20during%20the%20hearing%20of%20Sisodia%E2%80%99s%20plea%20against%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%E2%80%99s%20dismissal%20of%20his%20bail%20pleas%2C%20the%20apex%20court%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fno-money-has-come-to-manish-sisodia-how-will-you-bring-him-under-pmla-sc-to-ed%5C%22%3Eexpressed%3C%2Fa%3E%20doubts%20over%20the%20case.%20Earlier%20this%20month%2C%20it%20asked%20the%20CBI%20and%20ED%20as%20to%20how%20they%20seek%20to%20%E2%80%9Cestablish%20money%20laundering%20by%20Manish%20Sisodia%2C%20factually%20and%20legally%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20dismissing%20the%20application%20for%20bail%2C%20Justice%20Khanna%20said%20that%20the%20court%20has%20made%20%E2%80%9Cone%20pointed%20observation%E2%80%9D%20on%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20investigation%20agencies%20have%20assured%20the%20court%20that%20the%20trial%20will%20be%20concluded%20within%20%E2%80%9Csix%20to%20eight%20months.%E2%80%9D%20The%20bench%20also%20said%20that%20Sisodia%20will%20be%20entitled%20to%20apply%20for%20bail%20according%20to%20how%20the%20trial%20progresses.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20within%20three%20months%2C%20if%20the%20trial%20proceeds%20sloppily%20or%20slowly%2C%20he%E2%80%99ll%20be%20entitled%20to%20file%20an%20application%20for%20bail%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698652861000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30132930%2FFnUmsIjWAAEE9Es.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-manish-sisodia-bail%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'Within%20three%20months%2C%20if%20the%20trial%20proceeds%20sloppily%20or%20slowly%2C%20he'll%20be%20entitled%20to%20file%20an%20application%20for%20bail.'%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Anupam%3A%20Anil%20%26amp%3B%20I%20avoid%20discussing%20Satish%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698652761000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104819284%2Cimgsize-43270.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fanupam-kher-reveals-he-and-anil-kapoor-consciously-avoid-discussing-satish-kaushik-when-they