obs-than-counterparts-in-us-uk-germany%2Farticleshow%2F104817721.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BSycophants...%26quot%3B%3A%20Visva-Bharati%20Vice-Chancellor's%20Letter%20To%20Mamata%20Banerjee%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%20explosive%20letter%20mentioning%20the%20latest%20case%20surrounding%20Trinamool%20MP%20Mahua%20Moitra%20and%20the%20arrest%20of%20party%20leaders%20has%20become%20the%20latest%20bone%20of%20contention%20between%20the%20Visva%20Bharati%20administration%20and%20the%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVice-Chancellor%20Bidyut%20Chakraborty's%20letter%20to%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20came%20loaded%20with%20political%20statements%20on%20issues%20completely%20unrelated%20to%20Visva-Bharati%20after%20Ms%20Banerjee%20objected%20to%20a%20plaque%20not%20mentioning%20Rabindranath%20Tagore's%20name%20at%20Shantiniketan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20is%20an%20attempt%20to%20earn%20brownie%20points%20from%20the%20central%20government%20as%20Mr%20Chakraborty%20is%20seeking%20an%20extension%2C%20Trinamool%20has%20hit%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShantiniketan%2C%20where%20the%20Nobel%20laureate%20had%20built%20Visva-Bharati%20over%20a%20century%20ago%2C%20recently%20made%20it%20to%20the%20list%20of%20UNESCO%20World%20Heritage%20sites.%20A%20plaque%20unveiled%20to%20commemorate%20this%20honour%20triggered%20a%20controversy%20as%20it%20reportedly%20mentioned%20the%20names%20of%20the%20Vice%20Chancellor%20and%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20but%20not%20of%20Tagore.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20insults%20Tagore%20and%20belittles%20the%20anti-colonial%20heritage-creating%20efforts%20of%20our%20Nation's%20founding%20fathers.%20The%20central%20government%20will%20be%20well%20advised%20to%20remove%20this%20narcissistic%20display%20of%20arrogant%20self-exhibitionism%20forthwith%2C%20and%20to%20give%20Gurudev%20the%20tribute%20that%20the%20country%20owes%20to%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Banerjee%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Vice%20Chancellor%2C%20in%20his%20response%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20need%20to%20follow%20the%20ASI%20instructions%20while%20preparing%20the%20plaque%20and%20we%20are%20doing%20it%2C%20the%20result%20of%20which%20will%20soon%20be%20visible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20did%20not%20stop%20there.%20%26quot%3BMadam%2C%20please%20be%20magnanimous%20because%20you%20are%20as%20much%20a%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20your%20loyalists%20as%20others%20who%20may%20not%20always%20be%20your%20sycophants...A%20megalomaniac%20Rajya%20Sabha%20member%20of%20your%20political%20party%20tried%20to%20gain%20this%20recognition%20and%20the%20then%20Prime%20Minister%20also%20tried%20without%2C%20of%20course%2C%20success%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20Mr%20Chakraborty.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20went%20further%20to%20defend%20his%20administration%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20also%20here%20in%20the%20campus%20competent%20individuals%20who%20are%20completely%20different%20from%20the%20sycophants%20surrounding%20you...The%20Hon'ble%20Prime%20Minister%20is%20our%20Hon'ble%20Chancellor%20and%20his%20role%20in%20getting%20this%20World%20Heritage%20tag%20cannot%20be%20gauged%20in%20any%20of%20the%20available%20yardsticks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVisva-Bharati%20is%20the%20only%20central%20university%20which%20has%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20as%20its%20chancellor.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Chakraborty%20also%20sought%20to%20remind%20her%20how%20former%20Trinamool%20ministers%20are%20languishing%20in%20jails%20and%20about%20Mahua%20Moitra%2C%20who%20is%20being%20probed%20by%20the%20Ethics%20Committee%20of%20the%20Parliament%20over%20allegations%20of%20allowing%20a%20businessman%20drafts%20questions%20on%20behalf%20of%20her%20in%20exchange%20of%20gifts.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTwo%20of%20your%20senior%20ministers%20are%20in%20jail%3B%20some%20of%20your%20trusted%20aides%20(even%20from%20Birbhum)%20in%20jail%2C%20including%20in%20Tihar%20jail%20in%20Delhi.%20Your%20most%20vocal%20member%20of%20parliament%20is%20being%20charged%20with%20activities%20which%20have%20already%20drawn%20the%20parliamentary%20ethics%20committee%20to%20examine%20the%20issue%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20letter%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20purged%20Visva-Bharati%20of%20evil%20forces%20involved%20in%20activities%20which%20stand%20in%20contradiction%20with%20Visva-Bharati's%20ethos%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Vice%20Chancellor%20said.%20%26quot%3BVisva-Bharati%20was%20a%20nursery%20of%20corruption.%20By%20dint%20of%20hard%20work%2C%20it%20has%20now%20changed%2C%20and%20we%20are%20sure%2C%20in%20course%20of%20time%2C%20we%20will%20see%20the%20results%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20letter%2C%20Mr%20Chakraborty%20also%20raised%20the%20issue%20of%20a%20road%20passing%20through%20the%20university%20but%20is%20under%20the%20possession%20of%20the%20government.%20%26quot%3BA%20face-to-face%20dialogue%20with%20us%20will%20give%20you%20an%20opportunity%20to%20see%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20narrative%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Vice-Chancellor%20had%20earlier%20clashed%20with%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20over%20the%20property%20dispute%20between%20Nobel%20Laureate%20Amartya%20Sen%20and%20the%20university.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20NDTV%20on%20your%20chat.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698651600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fc590iok8_bidyut-chakraborty-and-mamata-banerjee-_625x300_30_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvisva-bharati-vice-chancellor-bidyut-chakrabortys-explosive-letter-to-mamata-banerjee-4526999%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20explos