ith%20love%20and%20admiration%20in%20the%20comments.%20Malaika%20also%20shared%20a%20series%20of%20pictures%20and%20a%20heartfelt%20note%20expressing%20gratitude%20for%20her%20life.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fmalaika-arora-goes-skydiving-alone-on-her-birthday-says-she-jumped-into-48-with-a-bang-watch-video%2Farticleshow%2F104818606.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Two-State%20Solution%20Only%20Way%20To%20End%20Gaza%20War%3A%20Lebanon%20Envoy%20To%20NDTV%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECalling%20the%20ongoing%20Israel-Hamas%20war%20worrisome%2C%20Lebanese%20Ambassador%20to%20India%20Rabie%20Narsh%20said%20that%20the%20two-state%20solution%20is%20the%20only%20way%20to%20end%20the%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20NDTV%2C%20Dr%20Narsh%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20situation%20didn't%20start%20on%20October%207%2C%20the%20crisis%20has%20been%20there%20since%201967.%20Since%20then%2C%20Israel%20has%20been%20refusing%20all%20peace%20initiatives%20and%20has%20been%20inflicting%20horrendous%20damages%20on%20the%20Palestinians.%20The%20only%20way%20out%20of%20this%20violence%20is%20the%202-state%20solution.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20of%20a%20two-state%20solution%20--%20with%20a%20sovereign%20Palestinian%20state%20alongside%20Israel%20and%20Jerusalem%20as%20their%20shared%20capital%20--%20has%20been%20the%20cornerstone%20of%20decades%20of%20international%20diplomacy%20aimed%20at%20ending%20the%20Israeli-Palestinian%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDr%20Narsh%20said%20that%20the%20Arab%20world%2C%20the%20United%20Nations%2C%20and%20several%20other%20countries%20have%20been%20pushing%20for%20the%20two-state%20solution%2C%20but%20Israel%20has%20not%20backed%20any%20of%20the%20peace%20initiatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20(Israel)%20does%20not%20abide%20by%20the%20UN%20resolutions.%20It%20has%20been%20denying%20all%20calls%20for%20a%20two-state%20solution.%20The%20Arab%20world%20was%20ready%20to%20restore%20ties%20with%20Israel%20if%20they%20restored%20sovereignty%20to%20Palestine.%20But%20it%20deprives%20them%20of%20basic%20rights%2C%20Palestineans%20have%20no%20dignity%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Narsh%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20tightened%20its%20blockade%20and%20bombardment%20of%20Gaza%20since%20Hamas%20gunmen%20stormed%20into%20Israel%20on%20October%207.%20Israeli%20authorities%20say%20the%20militants%20killed%20some%201%2C400%20people%20and%20took%20at%20least%20239%20hostages.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20country%20has%20also%20been%20striking%20%26quot%3BHezbollah%20terrorist%20targets%20in%20Lebanon%26quot%3B%2C%20which%20it%20claims%20is%20in%20retaliation%20to%20rocket%20fire.%20Cross-border%20exchanges%20with%20Hezbollah%20have%20become%20an%20almost%20daily%20occurrence%20since%20October%207%2C%20according%20to%20Israeli%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDr%20Narsh%20though%20claimed%20that%20the%20attacks%20are%20being%20initiated%20by%20Israel%20and%20Lebanon%20is%20not%20interested%20in%20a%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAny%20war%20needs%20two%20parties%20and%20Lebanon%20is%20not%20interested%20in%20a%20war.%20But%20Israel%20has%20been%20provoking%20Lebanon%20and%20Hezbollah%20along%20the%20border.%20They%20have%20been%20bombing%20homes%20and%20have%20killed%20civilians%2C%20and%20journalists%20in%20Lebanon%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIsrael%20believes%20that%20it%20is%20above%20international%20law.%20and%20this%20has%20to%20stop%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Narsh%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20on%20the%20October%207%20attack%2C%20the%20Lebanese%20envoy%20said%20that%20Hamas%20does%20not%20represent%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20and%20was%20only%20a%20result%20of%20the%20Israeli%20occupation%20of%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHamas%20does%20not%20represent%20Palestinian%20people.%20Hamas%20is%20just%20a%20militant%20group%2C%20resisting%20for%20their%20land.%20Wherever%20there%20is%20occupation%2C%20resistance%20is%20guaranteed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20military%20today%20said%20it%20had%20struck%20over%20600%20militant%20targets%20over%20the%20past%20few%20days%20as%20it%20continued%20to%20expand%20ground%20operations%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20where%20Palestinian%20civilians%20are%20in%20dire%20need%20of%20fuel%2C%20food%2C%20and%20clean%20water%20as%20the%20conflict%20enters%20its%20fourth%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698651240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fok8su0vc_rabie-narsh_625x300_30_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-war-two-state-solution-only-way-to-end-gaza-war-lebanon-envoy-to-ndtv-4527044%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Calling%20the%20ongoing%20Israel-Hamas%20war%20worrisome%2C%20Lebanese%20Ambassador%20to%20India%20Rabie%20Narsh%20said%20that%20the%20two-state%20solution%20is%20the%20only%20way%20to%20end%20the%20conflict.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-war-two-state-solution-only-way-to-end-gaza-war-lebanon-envoy-to-ndtv-4527044%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-war-two-state-solution-only-way-to-end-gaza-war-lebanon-envoy-to-ndtv-4527044%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-war-two-state-solution-only-way-to-end-gaza-war-lebanon-envoy-to-ndtv-4527044%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sena%20vs%20Sena%3A%20SC%20directs%20Speaker%20to%20conclude%20proceedings%20Dec%2031%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698651236000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104818425%2Cimgsize-138530.cms%