rmat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22682%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20Amazon%20software%20developer%20sits%20at%20a%20desk%20during%20a%20press%20event%20at%20the%20online%20retailer's%20research%20and%20development%20site.%3Cp%3ESebastian%20Kahnert%2Fpicture%20alliance%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3EAmazon%20Web%20Services%20certifications%20are%20titles%20granted%20to%20professionals%20who%20complete%20exams.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThere%20are%20different%20AWS%20paths%20focused%20on%20developers%2C%20networks%20and%20systems%2C%20data%20analytics%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20most%20general%20path%20is%20the%20Cloud%20Practitioner%20path.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-slack-channel-performance-plans-focus-pivot-shut-down-2023-10%5C%22%3EAmazon%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%26quot%3BAWS%20Certification%20helps%20learners%20build%20credibility%20and%20confidence%20by%20validating%20their%20cloud%20expertise%20with%20an%20industry-recognized%20credential%20and%20helps%20organizations%20identify%20skilled%20professionals%20to%20lead%20cloud%20initiatives%20using%20AWS.%26quot%3B%20That's%20a%20mouthful%20%E2%80%94%20let's%20unpack%20what%20it%20means.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhat%20is%20AWS%20certification%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20AWS%20certification%20is%20a%20title%20granted%20to%20people%20who%20successfully%20complete%20an%20exam%20that%20they%20can%20then%20use%20on%20business%20cards%2C%20email%20footers%2C%20letterhead%2C%20and%20anywhere%20else.%20AWS%20is%20short%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-cloud-industry-growth-laggard-microsoft-ai-google-2023-4%5C%22%3EAmazon%20Web%20Service%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Amazon's%20examinations%20involve%20specific%20areas%20of%20AWS%20which%20are%20called%20paths.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20paths%20include%20the%20Cloud%20Practitioner%20Path%2C%20which%20is%20the%20most%20general%20certification%3B%20the%20Architect%20Path%2C%20which%20is%20ideal%20for%20people%20who%20want%20to%20create%20applications%20on%20AWS%3B%20the%20Operations%20Path%2C%20which%20is%20a%20good%20choice%20for%20those%20who%20want%20to%20work%20with%20AWS%20networks%20and%20systems%3B%20the%20Developer%20Path%2C%20which%20leads%20toward%20software%20development%20and%20applications%3B%20and%20several%20others%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Data%20Analytics%20path%20and%20the%20Security%20path.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnly%20you%20can%20answer%20the%20question%20of%20the%20best%20AWS%20certification%20for%20your%20career%2C%20but%20there%20are%20some%20clues%20for%20you%20to%20follow%2C%20of%20course.%20Consider%20the%20jobs%20you%20hope%20to%20secure%20in%20the%20future%20and%20then%20work%20backward%20to%20see%20which%20path%20would%20logically%20lead%20to%20more%20opportunities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20much%20does%20it%20cost%20to%20get%20AWS%20certified%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20range%20of%20prices%20depending%20on%20which%20test%20you'll%20be%20taking.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20Cloud%20Practitioner%20exam%20is%20%24100%2C%20while%20associate-level%20exams%20cost%20%24150.%20And%20professional-level%20and%20Specialty%20exams%20are%20%24300.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20also%20learn%20AWS%20for%20free.%20In%20the%20words%20of%20Amazon%20Web%20Services%20itself%3A%20%26quot%3BAWS%20Educate%20provides%20hundreds%20of%20hours%20of%20free%2C%20self-paced%20training%2C%20resources%2C%20and%20labs%20specifically%20designed%20for%20the%20new-to-the-cloud%20learner.%26quot%3B%20There%20will%20still%20be%20the%20fees%20when%20you%20go%20for%20your%20actual%20certification%2C%20of%20course.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20are%20going%20after%20competitive%20IT%20jobs%2C%20then%20an%20AWS%20certification%20may%20well%20be%20worth%20the%20expense%2C%20time%2C%20and%20effort.%20While%20these%20certifications%20alone%20will%20not%20get%20you%20hired%20%E2%80%94%20only%20demonstrated%20ability%20and%20experience%20will%20do%20that%20%E2%80%94%20one%20may%20be%20the%20difference%20between%20you%20and%20an%20equally%20suitable%20applicant%20who%20has%20not%20completed%20an%20AWS%20certification.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20an%20AWS%20certificate%20hard%20to%20get%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20word%2C%20yes.%20With%20lots%20of%20study%20and%20practice%2C%20competent%20IT%20workers%20will%20pass%20these%20exams%20and%20get%20certified%2C%20but%20the%20preparation%20can%20be%20grueling%2C%20and%20the%20actual%20tests%20are%20a%20challenge.%20That's%20because%20they%20are%20not%20matters%20of%20rote%20memorization%3B%20rather%2C%20the%20tests%20are%20more%20problem-focused%2C%20wherein%20conditions%20are%20presented%20to%20you%20that%20simulate%20real-world%20scenarios%20you%20must%20tackle%20under%20tight%20time%20constraints.%20The%20more%20you%20prep%2C%20the%20better%20it%20will%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20AWS%20will%20often%20require%20programming%2C%20it%20does%20not%20require%20coding.%20While%20of%20course%2C%20a%20solid%20grounding%20in%20coding%20will%20help%20you%20immensely%20with%20AWS%20(and%20the%20rest%20of%20your%20IT%20work)%2C%20it%20is%20not%20a%20necessity%20for%20AWS%20certification%20or%20using%20the%20actual%20AWS%20cloud%20computing%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20long%20does%20an%20AWS%20certification%20last%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYour%20AWS%20certification%20will%20be%20valid%20for%20three%20years.%20After%20that%2C%20you%20need%20to%20be%20recertified.%20Amazon%20claims%20%26quot%3Brecertification%20helps%20strengthen%20the%20overall%20value%20of%20your%20AWS%20Certification%20and%20shows%20individuals%20and%20employers%20that%20your%20credential%20covers%20the%20latest%20AWS%20knowledge%2C%20skills%2C%20and%20best%20practices.%26quot%3B%20Still%2C%20we%20also%20suspect%20they%20may%20like%20charging%20you%20to%20take%20anothe