olises%20faith%2C%20New%20York%20City%20Mayor%20Eric%20Adams%20said%2C%20as%20he%20described%20the%20recent%20attacks%20and%20hate%20crimes%20against%20the%20community%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cstain%E2%80%9D%20on%20the%20country%20and%20vowed%20to%20protect%20its%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20gave%20a%20clarion%20call%20for%20educating%20people%20about%20Sikhism.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20are%20not%20about%20terror%3B%20you%20are%20about%20protector.%20That%20is%20what%20needs%20to%20be%20taught%20throughout%20this%20entire%20city.%20Our%20young%20people%20need%20to%20know%20that%2C%20our%20adults%20need%20to%20know%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20Adams%20said%20while%20addressing%20members%20of%20the%20Sikh%20community%20at%20the%20Baba%20Makhan%20Shah%20Lubana%20Sikh%20Center%20in%20the%20Queens%20neighbourhood%20of%20South%20Richmond%20Hill.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDescribing%20the%20Sikh%20community%20as%20an%20%E2%80%9Canchor%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20Richmond%20Hill%20neighbourhood%2C%20Adams%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CYour%20turban%20does%20not%20mean%20terrorism.%20It%20means%20protecting%2C%20it%20means%20community%2C%20it%20means%20family%2C%20it%20means%20faith%2C%20it%20means%20city%2C%20it%20means%20us%20coming%20together.%20We%20will%20change%20the%20dialogue%20and%20narrative%20with%20you.%20We%20can%20do%20it%20together.%E2%80%9D%20Adams%20and%20New%20York%20State%20Assemblywoman%20Jenifer%20Rajkumar%20met%20and%20addressed%20members%20of%20the%20Sikh%20community%20here%20Sunday%2C%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20recent%20incidents%20of%20hate%20crime%20and%20assault%20against%20Sikhs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20October%2015%2C%20a%2019-year-old%20Sikh%20boy%20was%20attacked%20by%20Christopher%20Philippeaux%2C%2026%2C%20while%20he%20was%20riding%20the%20bus%20in%20Richmond%20Hill.%20Philippeaux%20punched%20the%20Sikh%20teenager%20in%20the%20back%20of%20the%20head%2C%20tried%20to%20knock%20off%20his%20turban%20and%20told%20him%20%E2%80%9CWe%20don't%20wear%20that%20in%20this%20country.%E2%80%9D%20Philippeaux%20has%20been%20charged%20with%20assault%20as%20a%20hate%20crime%20and%20aggravated%20harassment%2C%20Queens%20District%20Attorney%20Melinda%20Katz%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWithin%20days%20of%20this%20assault%2C%2066-year-old%20Jasmer%20Singh%20was%20attacked%20when%20his%20car%20collided%20with%20another%20vehicle.%20The%20driver%20of%20the%20other%20car%2C%2030-year-old%20Gilbert%20Augustin%2C%20allegedly%20punched%20the%20elderly%20Sikh%20man%20three%20times%20in%20the%20head%20and%20face%20and%20Singh%20later%20succumbed%20to%20his%20injuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDescribing%20the%20attack%20against%20Singh%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cviolent%20senseless%20act%2C%E2%80%9D%20Adams%20said%20%E2%80%9CJasmer%20should%20still%20be%20with%20us.%20He%20should%20still%20be%20with%20his%20son.%20He%20should%20still%20be%20living%20out%20the%20American%20dream%2C%20watching%20his%20son%2C%20who's%20now%20an%20immigration%20attorney.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20should%20still%20be%E2%80%A6part%20of%20this%20community.%20That%20dream%20turned%20into%20a%20nightmare%20the%20other%20day%20when%20his%20life%20was%20taken%20from%20us%20prematurely%2C%E2%80%9D%20Adams%20said%2C%20flanked%20by%20Singh's%20son%20Subeg%20Singh%20Multani%20and%20other%20members%20of%20the%20Sikh%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDescribing%20Sikhs%20as%20%E2%80%9Cprotectors%E2%80%9D%20of%20society%2C%20Rajkumar%20asserted%20that%20the%20hateful%20targeting%20of%20Sikhs%20is%20%26quot%3Bnot%20acceptable%E2%80%9D%20and%20perpetrators%20of%20such%20violence%20will%20be%20prosecuted%20to%20the%20fullest%20extent%20of%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20the%20first%20time%2C%20we%20are%20going%20to%20use%20the%20levers%20of%20government%20to%20end%20hate%20crimes%20against%20Sikh%20Americans.%20For%20the%20first%20time%2C%20we%20are%20going%20to%20come%20together%20and%E2%80%A6educate%E2%80%A6New%20York%20State%2C%20the%20United%20States%20and%20the%20entire%20world%20about%20who%20the%20Sikh%20people%20truly%20are%20so%20we%20are%20not%20attacked%20and%20misunderstood%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rajkumar%2C%20the%20first%20Indian-American%20woman%20elected%20to%20New%20York%20State%20Office%20and%20who%20described%20herself%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdaughter%20of%20Punjab%E2%80%9D%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERajkumar%20said%20this%20was%20not%20the%20first%20time%20she%20had%20visited%20the%20Gurudwara%20and%20had%20spoken%20out%20against%20hate%20crimes.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20it%20is%20the%20last%20time%20I%20want%20to%20be%20standing%20here%20speaking%20out%20against%20hate%20crimes.%20Starting%20now%20we%20are%20going%20to%20end%20the%20hateful%20targeting%20of%20Sikhs%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20behalf%20of%20herself%20and%20the%20Sikh%20community%2C%20Rajkumar%20presented%20the%20Mayor%20with%20a%20%E2%80%98Kirpan'%2C%20a%20mandatory%20article%20of%20faith%20in%20Sikhism.%20The%20sword%2C%20engraved%20with%20the%20words%20%E2%80%9CNew%20York%20City%20Mayor%20Adams%20is%20our%20protector%E2%80%9D%2C%20is%20%E2%80%9Cto%20embolden%20you%20in%20your%20fight%20for%20our%20Sikh%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rajkumar%20said%20to%20Adams%2C%20amid%20slogans%20of%20%E2%80%98Bole%20So%20Nihaal%2C%20Sat%20Sri%20Akal'.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAdams%20said%20the%20sword%20is%20a%20symbol%20of%20how%20as%20the%20mayor%2C%20he%20must%20be%20the%20protector%20of%20the%20Sikh%20community.%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20when%20a%20member%20of%20your%20community%20is%20harmed%2C%20I%20take%20full%20responsibility%20(for)%20that.%E2%80%9D%20Multani%2C%20who%20became%20emotional%20and%20choked%20up%20as%20he%20addressed%20the%20gathering%2C%20said%20his%20father%20came%20from%20India%20to%20the%20US%20in%20the%20early%201990s%20with%20the%20American%20dream%20in%20his%20eyes.%20%26quot%3BWe%20didn't%20know%20that%20the%20dream%20would%20be%20shattered%20the%20way%20it%20has%20shattered%E2%80%9D%20on%20October%2019%20in%20this%20%E2%80%9Cgreat%E2%80%9D%20and%20diverse%20city%20of%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMultani%20said%20his%20father%20lived%20in%20Richmond%20Hill%20all%20his%20life%20because%20he%20considered%20the%20neighbourhood%20his%20home.%20Multani%20%E2%80%9Cpleaded%E2%80%9D%20that%20the%20Mayor%20and%20city%20officials%20take%20%E2%80%9Cstrong%20measures%E2%80%9D%20to%20ensure%20the%20safety%20of%20the%20Sikh%20community%20so%20that%20no%20other%20person%20suffers%20the%20loss%20he%20is%20enduring.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20love%20everyone%2C%20we%20love%20every%20other%20minority.%20But%20why%20we%20are%20being%20targeted%3F%20That%20is%20the%20question.%20We%20are%20law-abiding%20citizens%20of%20the%20United%20States.%20We%20love%20this%20country%20as%20much%20as%20others%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20Multani%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMultani%20said%20he%20is%20constantly%20in%20contact%20with%20the%20Queens%20District%20Attorney%20and%20officials%20regarding%20the%20case.%20He%20called%20on%20members%20of%20the%20Sikh%20community%20to%20accompany%20him%20when%20Augustin%20is%20arraigned%20on%20October%2031.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20requesting%20everyone%20to%20join%20me%20that%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20with%20their%20turbans%20on%2C%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20will%20show%20solidarity%20and%20unity%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20judge.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20can%20show%20them%20this%20is%20a%20hate%20crime.%20This%20case%20must%20be%20pursued%20as%20a%20hate%20crime.%E2%80%9D%20Adams%20said%20that%20to%20lose%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Sikh%20community%20in%20this%20magnitude%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bstain%20on%20our%20entire%20city%20and%20nation%2C%20because%20the%20hate%20we%20are%20seeing%20because%20your%20symbol%20of%20faith%20is%20not%20only%20localised%20to%20New%20York%20City%2C%20we%20are%20seeing%20similar%20acts%20across%20the%20entire%20country.%E2%80%9D%20He%20recalled%20that%20after%209%2F11%2C%20Sikhs%20were%20%E2%80%9Cunder%20attack%20over%20and%20over%20again%20because%20of%20the%20lack%20of%20understanding%20of%20what%20your%20turban%20represents.%E2%80%9D%20Rajkumar%20noted%20that%20the%20recent%20attacks%20against%20Sikhs%20are%20part%20of%20a%20nationwide%20trend%3A%20in%202021%2C%20the%20most%20recent%20year%20for%20which%20data%20is%20available%2C%20documented%20hate%20crimes%20against%20the%20Sikh%20community%20increased%20140%25%20across%20the%20country.%20Hate%20crimes%20have%20been%20frequent%20in%20the%20Richmond%20Hill%20area%2C%20her%20office%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERajkumar%20demanded%20that%20incidents%20of%20hate%20against%20Sikhs%20must%20be%20stopped.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20our%20fight%20for%20civil%20rights.%20This%20is%20our%20demand.%20Stop%20the%20targeting%20of%20Sikh%20Americans%20and%20see%20the%20Sikhs%20for%20who%20we%20really%20are%20-%20the%20protectors%20of%20society%2C%20proud%20Americans%20with%20generous%20hearts.%E2%80%9D%20Adams%20said%20there%20must%20be%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfull%20frontal%20assault%20on%20ending%20hate%E2%80%A6What%20plays%20out%20across%20the%20globe%20by%20other%20doers%20is%20being%20attached%20to%20your%20community.%20We%20need%20to%20clearly%20educate%20people%20about%20what%20this%20community%20stands%20for%20and%20what%20you%20represent.%E2%80%9D%20He%20recalled%20how%20the%20Sikh%20community%2C%20during%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic%2C%20had%20fed%20millions%20of%20people%20without%20asking%20about%20their%20backgrounds%2C%20economic%20status%20or%20religion.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20came%20here%20and%20watched%20in%20awe%20as%20you%20opened%20your%20doors%20when%20the%20hearts%20of%20many%20were%20closed.%20You%20were%20truly%20protectors%20during%20the%20most%20difficult%20time.%20It%20is%20our%20obligation%20to%20join%20you%20as%20you%20protect%20your%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20Adams%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%