20Hotels%20%26amp%3B%20Resorts%20Pvt.%20Ltd.%2C%20Vardha%20Enterprises%20Pvt.%20Ltd.%20and%20its%20directors%20and%20promoters%20Shiv%20Shankar%20Sharma%2C%20Rattan%20Kant%20Sharma%20and%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20had%20seized%20Rs%201.2%20crore%20in%20cash%20during%20the%20searches%20last%20month.%20The%20Triton%20group%2C%20it%20is%20alleged%2C%20received%20investment%20from%20a%20Mauritius%20entity%20back%20in%202007-2008.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20is%20likely%20to%20question%20Vaibhav%20Gehlot%20on%20his%20alleged%20links%20with%20Rattan%20Kant%20Sharma.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBrushing%20off%20the%20allegations%20against%20his%20son%2C%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20said%20that%20Vaibhav%20has%20no%20foreign%20exchange%20dealings.%20%26quot%3BVaibhav%20Gehlot%20only%20has%20a%20taxi%20company.%20Rattan%20(Kant%20Sharma)%20was%20a%20partner%2C%20but%20they%20work%20separately%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Rajasthan%20Chief%20Minister%20said%20central%20agencies%20have%20lost%20their%20credibility%20due%20to%20the%20alleged%20misuse%20by%20BJP-led%20central%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCentral%20agencies%20have%20no%20credibility%20now.%20It%20is%20a%20worrying%20situation.%20This%20is%20not%20about%20my%20son%20or%20the%20state%20Congress%20president.%20Aatank%20macha%20rakha%20hai%20desh%20mein%20(they%20have%20spread%20terror%20in%20the%20country)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Gehlot%20also%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20central%20agence%20for%20issuing%20a%20short%20notice%20summons.%20%26quot%3BIs%20this%20a%20joke%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3Cbr%3E%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698647460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-04%2Frnfrgalg_vaibhav-gehlot_625x300_09_April_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fashok-gehlot-vaibhav-gehlot-rajasthan-polls-ed-congress-bjp-ashok-gehlots-son-appears-before-probe-agency-in-delhi-4526838%22%2C%22