20dead%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698647363000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104816110%2Cimgsize-40432.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fmalayalam%2F35-year-old-malayalam-actress-renjusha-menon-found-dead-at-her-residence%2Farticleshow%2F104816110.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Renjusha%20is%20a%20well-recognized%20figure%20in%20the%20entertainment%20industry%2C%20known%20for%20her%20appearances%20in%20various%20movies%20and%20TV%20serials.%20In%20her%20most%20recent%20work%2C%20she%20took%20on%20a%20leading%20role%20in%20the%20show%20'Aanandaragam%2C'%20whereas%20she%20showcased%20her%20comedic%20talent%20in%20the%20sitcom%20'Varan%20Doctaranu.'%20Her%20portrayals%20in%20'Ente%20Mathavu%2C'%20'Mrs.%20Hitler%2C'%20and%20other%20television%20programs%20have%20garnered%20considerable%20acclaim.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22etimes.in%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fmalayalam%2F35-year-old-malayalam-actress-renjusha-menon-found-dead-at-her-residence%2Farticleshow%2F104816110.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Review%3A%20Paradise%20-%20Beautifully%20Realised%20Drama%20Is%20Beyond%20Masterful%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUnswerving%20in%20its%20grasp%20of%20both%20philosophy%20and%20psychology%2C%20Prasanna%20Vithanage's%20%3Cem%3EParadise%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20a%20masterly%20evocation%20of%20the%20frailty%20of%20'man'%20when%20faced%20with%20a%20crisis.%20A%20nation%20totters%20on%20the%20brink%20of%20economic%20ruination%2C%20a%20relationship%20drifts%20into%20a%20grey%20zone%20and%20both%20morality%20and%20humanity%20are%20put%20to%20the%20test%20in%20rapidly%20worsening%20circumstances.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EParadise%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20written%20by%20the%20veteran%20Sri%20Lankan%20director%20in%20collaboration%20with%20Anushka%20Senanayake%2C%20is%20an%20astute%2C%20incisive%20drama%20that%20centres%20on%20a%20marriage%20buffeted%20by%20events%20unfolding%20in%20the%20world%20outside.%20But%20it%20isn't%20just%20another%20ordinary%20tale%20of%20marital%20discord%20set%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bparadise%26quot%3B%20lost.%20%3Cem%3EParadise%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20an%20unblemished%20amalgam%20of%20multiple%20layers%20of%20consciousness%2C%20ranging%20from%20the%20timeless%20to%20the%20instantly%20tangible%2C%20from%20the%20hoary%20to%20the%20contemporaneous.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWinner%20of%20the%20Kim%20Jiseok%20Award%20at%20the%20Busan%20International%20Film%20Festival%2C%20Paradise%20had%20its%20South%20Asia%20premiere%20at%20the%20Mumbai%20Film%20Festival%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EProduced%20by%20Anto%20Chittilappilly's%20Newton%20Cinema%2C%20presented%20by%20Mani%20Ratnam's%20Madras%20Talkies%2C%20shot%20by%20Rajeev%20Ravi%2C%20edited%20by%20A.%20Sreekar%20Prasad%20and%20scored%20by%20composer%20K%20(K%20Krishna%20Kumar)%2C%20the%20Roshan%20Mathew-Dhanya%20Rajendra%20starrer%20makes%20liberal%20use%20of%20Sinhala%2C%20Malayalam%2C%20Hindi%20and%20English%20as%20languages%20intermingle%20in%20a%20beautifully%20orchestrated%20interplay%20of%20cultures%2C%20interpretations%20of%20mythology%20and%20intonations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVithanage's%20exquisite%20film%20it%20is%20an%20all-out%20exploration%20of%20turmoil%20within%20and%20turmoil%20without%20in%20a%20nation%20sitting%20on%20a%20powder%20keg.%20Public%20anger%20is%20at%20its%20peak%20and%2C%20as%20events%20take%20a%20disconcerting%20turn%2C%20a%20young%20Malayali%20couple%20on%20a%20Ramayana%20tour%20of%20Sri%20Lanka%20to%20celebrate%20their%20fifth%20wedding%20anniversary%2C%20accidentally%20run%20into%20the%20eye%20of%20the%20storm.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmritha%20(Darshana%20Rajendran)%2C%20a%20blogger%2C%20and%20Kesav%20(Roshan%20Mathew)%2C%20a%20filmmaker%2C%20are%20in%20the%20island%20nation%20two%20months%20after%20an%20economic%20downturn%20has%20triggered%20despair%20and%20disquiet%20all%20around%20amid%20shortages%20of%20essential%20commodities%2C%20fuel%20and%20electricity.%20What%20the%20couple%20encounters%20spans%20from%20the%20personal%20to%20the%20political%2C%20and%20from%20the%20intimate%20to%20the%20existential.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKesav%2C%20based%20in%20India's%20financial%20capital%20and%20awaiting%20a%20decision%20from%20a%20streaming%20platform%20on%20a%20project%20that%20he%20has%20pitched%2C%20is%20on%20tenterhooks.%20The%20couple's%20trip%20to%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20now%20cheaper%20to%20visit%20than%20at%20any%20other%20time%2C%20is%20to%20help%20the%20man%20take%20his%20mind%20off%20the%20professional%20imponderables%20he%20is%20exercised%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20all%20seems%20to%20be%20smooth%20sailing%20as%20their%20driver%20and%20tour%20guide%20Andrew%20(Shyam%20Fernando)%20takes%20them%20to%20spots%20where%20crucial%20events%20of%20the%20Ramayana%20are%20said%20to%20have%20occurred%20and%20fills%20them%20in%20with%20a%20wealth%20of%20mythic%20stories.%20They%20are%20then%20driven%20to%20a%20bungalow%20perched%20on%20a%20hill%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20lush%20forest.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETrouble%20erupts%20in%20this%20idyll%20and%20sets%20off%20a%20discomfiting%20chain%20of%20events%20that%20sends%20the%20couple%2C%20like%20the%20nation%20they%20are%20touring%2C%20into%20a%20tailspin.%20Amritha%20and%20Kesav%20react%20differently%20as%20matters%20escalate%20quickly.%20The%20choices%20they%20make%20lay%20bare%20the%20workings%20of%20their%20minds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20screenplay%20relies%20far%20less%20on%20words%20than%20on%20gestures%20and%20meaningful%20silences%20and%20expressions%20-%20the%20two%20lead%20actors%20are%20brilliantly%20understated.%20Much%20is%20left%20unsaid%2C%20a%20lot%20is%20articulated%20between%20the%20lines%2C%20and%20the%20underlying%20meanings%20of%20actions%20and%20reactions%20reveal%20themselves%20in%20all%20the%20opacity%20that%20humans%20are%20capable%20of%20when%20they%20are%20intent%20on%20self-preservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVithanage's%20layered%20examination%20of%20human%20behaviour%20is%20especially%20striking%20because%20he%20deals%20here%20with%20individuals%20who%20have%20no%20control%20over%20what%20is%20happening%20to%20them%20and%20around%20them.%20But%20Kesav%20thinks%20that%20his%20life%2C%20career%20and%20marriage%20are%20all%20poised%20for%20a%20turnround.%20The%20world%2C%20he%20seems%20to%20feel%2C%20revolves%20around%20him%20and%20that%20he%20has%20everything%20in%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmritha%2C%20sensitive%20and%20attuned%20to%20the%20beauty%20that%20she%20is%20surrounded%20by%20despite%20the%20upheavals%20that%20threaten%20the%20tranquility%20of%20the%20location%2C%20is%20acutely%20aware%20of%20the%20line%20that%20separates%20what%20is%20right%20from%20what%20is%20merely%20expedient.%20Within%20the%20marriage%2C%20the%20clear%20clash%20of%20ideals%20leads%20to%20a%20silent%20battle%20that%20ends%20explosively%2C%20and%20literally%20at%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FV4CB2px2Vso%3Fsi%3DSEf7bleQy2iOlrnU%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBesides%20Andrew%2C%20who%20sleeps%20in%20the%20driver's%20quarters%2C%20the%20tourist%20bungalow%20has%20two%20other%20occupants%20-%20the%20caretaker%20Shree%20(Sumith%20Ilango)%2C%20who%20has%20a%20hunting%20gun%20although%20he%20himself%20isn't%20a%20meat%20eater%2C%20and%20the%20cook%20Iqbal%20(Isham%20Samzudeen)%2C%20who%20revels%20in%20humming%20Hindi%20film%20songs%20as%20the%20night%20wears%20on%20in%20the%20woods.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EParadise%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20a%20beautifully%20realized%20drama%20about%20a%20nation%2C%20an%20economy%20and%20a%20people%20pushed%20into%20an%20abyss%20by%20the%20misgovernance%20of%20a%20political%20clan.%20Its%20repeated%20references%20to%20the%20Ramayana%20-%20Sri%20Lanka%20has%20over%2050%20sites%20that%20are%20associated%20with%20the%20Hindu%20epic%20-%20and%20the%20mass%20unrest%20in%20the%20nation%20serve%20as%20a%20backdrop%20for%20a%20story%20of%20two%20tourists.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECentral%20to%20the%20film%20are%20a%20midnight%20robbery%2C%20a%20theft%20of%20precious%20belongings%2C%20a%20police%20investigation%20led%20by%20Sergeant%20Bandara%20(Mahendra%20Perera)%2C%20the%20arrest%20of%20three%20men%20for%20a%20crime%20they%20may%20not%20have%20committed%2C%20custodial%20torture%20and%20brewing%20discontent.%20And%20there%20is%20a%20Sambar%20deer%20that%20becomes%20a%20bone%20of%20contention.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20Vithanage%2C%20best%20known%20for%20Death%20on%20a%20Full%20Moon%20Day%20and%20August%20Sun%20(both%20which%20are%20about%20people%20grappling%20with%20the%20repercussions%20of%20civil%20war%20and%20ethnic%20violence)%2C%20isn't%20given%20to%20simplistic%2C%20judgmental%20delineation%20of%20characters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20conflicting%20signals%20that%20he%20seamlessly%20weaves%20into%20the%20Paradise%20narrative%20without%20seeking%20to%20make%20anything%20too%20obvious%20is%20meant%20to%20spark%20questions%20more%20than%20provide%20answers.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20apparent%20answers%20that%20the%20film%20points%20towards%20-%20many%20of%20them%20are%20in%20response%20to%20questions%20related%20to%20gender%2C%20to%20Ravana%2C%20Lord%20Rama%2C%20Sita%20and%20the%20Agni%20Pareeksha%20she%20was%20subjected%20to%20-%20are%20only%20suggestions%20and%20not%20last%20words.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20storyline%20abounds%20in%20intriguing%20ambiguities%20as%20Vithanage%20approaches%20the%20problems%20that%20Amritha%20and%20Kesav%20encounter%20as%20they%20try%20to%20find%20a%20way%20around%20the%20crisis.%20They%20are%20led%20further%20and%20further%20into%20a%20quagmire%20in%20the%20process.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20man%20is%20pragmatic%20to%20the%20point%20of%20being%20self-serving.%20The%20woman's%20moral%20compass%2C%20in%20contrast%2C%20is%20intact.%20So%2C%20the%20issues%20that%20they%20grapple%20with%20are%20emotional%2C%20ethical%20and%20marital%20and%20the%20gap%20between%20how%20they%20view%20the%20world%20and%20what%20they%20want%20from%20it%20is%20a%20yawning%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20leads%20deliver%20impeccable%20performances%20that%20are%20marked%20by%20restraint%20and%20quiet%20power.%20Roshan%20Mathew%20is%20an%20epitome%20of%20poise%20even%20as%20he%20plays%20a%20man%20who%20appears%20to%20be%20amiable%20on%20the%20face%20of%20it%20but%2C%20when%20push%20comes%20to%20shove%2C%20has%20no%20qualms%20about%20making%20questionable%20moves.%20He%20modulates%20the%20shifts%20to%20perfection.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDarshana%20Rajendran%20is%20the%20core%20of%20%3Cem%3EParadise%3C%2Fem%3E.%20With%20her%20eyes%20alone%20she%20conveys%20a%20whole%20of%20world%20of%20emotions%20-%20joy%2C%20fear%2C%20doubt%2C%20agony%20-%20with%20minimal%20effort.%20Hers%20is%20a%20performance%20of%20astounding%20and%20enriching%20clarity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20film%20is%20about%20a%20world%20floundering%20in%20a%20deep%20hole%20and%20in%20need%20of%20healing%2C%20but%20in%20his%20%3Cem%3EParadise%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20writer%20and%20director%20Prasanna%20Vithanage%20ensures%20that%20nothing%20is%20amiss.%20It%20is%20beyond%20masterful.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698646740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F7kdcsdh_paradise_625x300_30_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fparadise-review-beautifully-realised-drama-is-beyond-masterful-4-5-stars-4526848%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Paradise%20Review%3A%20Paradise%2C%20a%20Busan%20International%20Film%20Festival%20winner%2C%20had%20its%20South%20Asia%20premiere%20at%20the%20Mumbai%20Film%20Festival%2