E2%80%99s%20Who%20in%20the%20Data%20%7C%20Ghasi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30100237%2F3100990738_7598ee7b2c_o-2.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBeyond%20politics%2C%20the%20Bihar%20caste%20survey%20is%20a%20revolutionary%20document.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EA%20public%20document%2C%20the%20first%20ever%20after%201931%2C%20allowing%20for%20people%20to%20stand%20up%20and%20be%20counted.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20go%20down%20to%20the%20wire%2C%20on%20what%20each%20of%20the%20numbers%20unveiled%20mean.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWho%20are%20the%20people%20referred%20to%20by%20percentages%20in%20the%20survey%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20start%20with%20Ghasi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20October%202%2C%20the%20state%20government%20in%20Bihar%20released%20a%20list%20of%20209%20castes%2C%20enumerating%20their%20names%20and%20populations%2C%20and%20their%20respective%20share%20in%20the%20total%20population.%20From%20a%20political%20perspective%2C%20it%20was%20not%20just%20a%20census%20but%20the%20beginning%20of%20a%20new%20era%20in%20politics%2C%20being%20referred%20to%20as%20Mandal%203.0.%20The%20survey%20has%20had%20a%20snowball%20effect%20on%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20politics%2C%20as%20the%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20government%20in%20Rajasthan%20announced%20that%20it%20will%20conduct%20a%20caste-based%20survey%20in%20the%20state%20just%20before%20the%20election%20notification%20was%20issued.%20The%20Congress%20party%20has%20also%20announced%20plans%20for%20caste-based%20surveys%20in%20other%20states.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20is%20yet%20to%20come%20up%20with%20something%20to%20counter%20this%20demand%20%E2%80%93%20it%20is%20neither%20able%20to%20oppose%20nor%20support%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHere%2C%20we%20will%20discuss%20the%20significance%20of%20the%20report%20released%20by%20the%20Bihar%20government.%20What%20are%20the%20traditions%20of%20these%20castes%3F%20How%20far%20do%20they%20extend%20and%20what%20is%20their%20status%20today%3F%20Although%20the%20social%20and%20economic%20status%20has%20not%20been%20released%20by%20the%20Bihar%20government%2C%20we%20will%20try%20to%20uncover%20these%20layers%20within%20the%20castes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20333px)%2085vw%2C%20333px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22333%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742.jpg%20838w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742-210x300.jpg%20210w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742-715x1024.jpg%20715w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682410%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22477%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EFirst%20of%20all%2C%20let%20us%20talk%20about%20a%20caste%20which%20has%20been%20considered%20one%20of%20the%20most%20politically%20powerful%20castes%20in%20Bihar%20since%20at%20least%201990%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Ghasi%20caste.%20It%20is%20ranked%2056%20in%20the%20report%20released%20by%20Bihar%20government%20and%20its%20total%20population%20is%20stated%20to%20be%20only%201%2C462%20people%2C%20that%20is%20only%200.0011%25%20of%20the%20total%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGhasi%20is%20historically%20a%20caste%20of%20shepherds.%20Unlike%20those%20shepherds%20who%20live%20like%20nomads%20with%20their%20sheep%2C%20goats%2C%20cattle%2C%20etc.%2C%20these%20are%20shepherds%20who%20have%20settled%20down%20in%20the%20plains.%20They%20are%20also%20called%20Ghasiyaras.%20The%20name%20is%20derived%20from%20the%20word%20for%20grass%2C%20which%20hints%20to%20their%20profession%20of%20the%20past%20%E2%80%93%20to%20chop%20and%20fetch%20grass%20to%20feed%20the%20cattle.%20The%20tradition%20of%20calling%20them%20Ghasi%20may%20have%20started%20when%20a%20group%20of%20nomadic%20herders%20decided%20to%20settle%20down%20for%20a%20secure%20and%20stable%20life.%20They%20must%20have%20had%20two%20things%20before%20them.%20Firstly%2C%20their%20cattle%20get%20fodder%20and%20water%2C%20and%20secondly%20they%20get%20land%20to%20grow%20grains%20to%20sustain%20themselves.%20In%20this%20way%2C%20the%20ancestors%20of%20this%20caste%20might%20have%20adopted%20farming%20and%20cattle%20rearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20circumstances%20have%20changed%20with%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%20of%20settling%20down%20in%20the%20plains%2C%20they%20must%20have%20gradually%20lost%20their%20tribal%20identity%2C%20which%20was%20replaced%20with%20a%20non-tribal%20identity.%20Ghasis%20are%20also%20called%20Ghoshi%20and%20Goshi.%20The%20meaning%20of%20these%20two%20words%20is%20not%20clearly%20defined%20anywhere%2C%20but%20in%20Hindi%20literature%20the%20term%20Ghoshi%20refers%20to%20%E2%80%98caller%E2%80%99%2C%20derived%20from%20the%20word%20Ghosh%20which%20means%20%E2%80%98to%20call%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20Ghoshi%20means%20%E2%80%98the%20one%20who%20calls%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20Bihar%2C%20this%20caste%20is%20spread%20over%20some%20areas%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20It%20is%20also%20a%20sub-caste%20of%20Yadavs.%20Many%20foreign%20historians%20%E2%80%93%20Horace%20Arthur%20Rose%2C%20Denzil%20Ibbetson%2C%20Edward%20Douglas%20MacLagan%2C%20etc.%20%E2%80%93%20have%20noted%20that%20the%20caste%20has%20both%20Hindu%20and%20Muslim%20members.%20Some%20historians%20believe%20that%20those%20Yadavs%20who%20converted%20to%20Islam%20were%20called%20Ghosi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20no%20one%20believes%20this%20now.%20Now%2C%20even%20those%20who%20were%20born%20in%20Ghosi%20families%20have%20started%20calling%20themselves%20Yadav%20instead%20of%20Ghosi.%20People%20of%20this%20caste%20are%20found%2C%20if%20only%20sporadically%2C%20in%20the%20Magadha%20region%20of%20Bihar.%20They%20also%20live%20in%20the%20districts%20of%20Mainpuri%2C%20Etawah%2C%20Hamirpur%2C%20Jhansi%2C%20Banda%2C%20Jalaun%2C%20Kanpur%2C%20Fatehpur%20etc.%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELike%20all%20Indian%20Hindu%20castes%20which%20are%20divided%20into%20%3Cem%3Egotras%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20people%20of%20the%20Ghasi%20caste%20are%20also%20divided%20into%20many%20gotras%20and%20even%20today%20they%20do%20not%20form%20marriage%20alliances%20outside%20their%20gotras.%20Some%20of%20these%20gotras%20are%20%E2%80%93%20Babariya%20or%20Barbaiya%2C%20Phatak%2C%20Jiwariya%20or%20Jarwariya%2C%20Fatkaalu%20or%20Fatkiyan%2C%20Karaiya%2C%20Shondele%2C%20Raut%2C%20Lahugaya%2C%20Angoori%2C%20Bhrigude%20or%20Bhrigudev%2C%20Gainduya%20or%20Guduya%2C%20Nigana%20and%20Dhoomar%20or%20Dhunr%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20people%20of%20this%20caste%20have%20many%20legends%20of%20their%20own%2C%20and%20in%20them%20the%20connection%20with%20Krishna%20is%20central.%20However%2C%20a%20big%20change%20has%20been%20witnessed%20now%20that%20everyone%20has%20come%20under%20the%20umbrella%20term%20Yadav.%20Therefore%2C%20no%20need%20is%20felt%20for%20a%20separate%20existence%20in%20the%20form%20of%20Ghasi%20or%20Ghosi.%20There%20are%20political%20reasons%20behind%20this%2C%20too.%20The%20politics%20of%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20in%20Bihar%20and%20Mulayam%20Singh%20Yadav%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20have%20come%20close%20to%20uniting%20all%20Yadavs.%20For%20this%20reason%2C%20they%20has%20become%20a%20big%20political%20force%20collectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Ghasi%20caste%20has%20been%20separately%20mentioned%20in%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20caste-based%20survey.%20It%20means%20there%20are%20still%20some%20people%20who%20do%20not%20like%20to%20call%20themselves%20Yadav.%20They%20are%20still%20Ghasi%2C%20the%20shepherds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENawal%20Kishor%20Kumar%20is%20the%20Hindi%20editor%20of%20Forward%20Press%2C%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698643846000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30100237%2F3100990738_7598ee7b2c_o-2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-ghasi%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Who%20are%20the%20people%20referred%20to%20by%20percentages%20in%20the%20survey%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-ghasi%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Citizens%20Have%20No%20Fundamental%20Right%20to%20Know%20of%20Source%20of%20Political%20Funding%3A%20AG%20to%20SC%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F18150906%2FSupreme-Court.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EAttorney%20General%20of%20India%20R.%20Venkataramani%20on%20Sunday%20(October%2029)%20submitted%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20that%20citizens%20have%20no%20fundamental%20right%20to%20know%20the%20sources%20of%20electoral%20bonds%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20AG%20was%20posting%20his%20views%20on%20petitions%20challenging%20the%20opaque%20nature%20of%20electoral%20bonds.%20The%20matter%20is%20posted%20for%20hearing%20in%20front%20of%20a%20Chief%20Justice%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud-led%20bench%20on%20October%2031.%20The%20bench%20also%20comprises%20Justices%C2%A0Sanjiv%20Khanna%2C%C2%A0B.R.%20Gavai%2C%C2%A0J.B.%20Pardiwala%20and%C2%A0Manoj%20Misra.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVenkataramani%20also%20said%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20would%20be%20entering%20the%20domain%20of%20policy%20if%20it%20tried%20to%20regulate%20electoral%20bonds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFirstly%2C%20there%20can%20be%20no%20general%20right%20to%20know%20anything%20and%20everything%20without%20being%20subjected%20to%20reasonable%20restrictions.%20Secondly%2C%20the%20right%20to%20know%20as%20necessary%20for%20expression%20can%20be%20for%20specific%20ends%20or%20purposes%20and%20not%20otherwise%2C%E2%80%9D%20AG%20said%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fcitizens-dont-have-right-to-information-regarding-funding-of-a-political-party-centre-tells-supreme-court-in-electoral-bonds-case-241137%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cb%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20just%20because%20courts%20have%20ruled%20that%20citizens%20have%20the%20right%20to%20know%20a%20candidate%E2%80%99s%20criminal%20antecedents%2C%20that%20cannot%20be%20extended%20to%20knowledge%20about%20funding%20through%20electoral%20bonds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%20does%20not%20infringe%20upon%20any%20individual%E2%80%99s%20rights%2C%20the%20AG%20continued%2C%20and%20cannot%20be%20said%20to%20be%20repugnant%20to%20any%20right%20under%20Part%20III%20of%20the%20Constitution.%3Cb%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20scheme%20in%20question%20extends%20the%20benefit%20of%20confidentiality%20to%20the%20contributor.%20It%20ensures%20and%20promotes%20clean%20money%20being%20contributed.%20It%20ensures%20abiding%20by%20tax%20obligations.%20Thus%2C%20it%20does%20not%20fall%20foul%20of%20any%20existing%20right.%20A%20constitutional%20Court%20reviews%20State%20action%20only%20if%20it%20impinges%20upon%20existing%20rights%20and%20not%20because%20State%20action%20has%20not%20provided%20for%20a%20possible%20right%20or%20an%20expectation%20howsoever%20desirable%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3Cb%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBackground%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20lead%20petition%2C%20filed%20by%20the%20Association%20of%20Democratic%20Reforms%20(ADR)%2C%20challenges%20the%20Finance%20Act%2C%202017%20which%20was%20enacted%20as%20a%20money%20bill%20and%20introduced%20the%20electoral%20bond%20scheme%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20electoral%20funding.%20The%20Act%20also%20removed%20the%20previous%20limit%20of%207.5%25%20of%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20average%20three-year%20net%20profit%20for%20political%20donations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20scheme%2C%20a%20company%20is%20not%20required%20to%20name%20the%20political%20parties%20to%20which%20such%20contributions%20are%20made.%20The%20donors%E2%80%99%20names%20are%20also%20not%20revealed%20to%20the%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioners%20argue%20that%20these%20amendments%20will%20result%20in%20opaqueness%2C%20heighten%20the%20odds%20of%20conflict%20of%20interest%20and%20also%20drastically%20increase%20black%20money%20and%20corruption.%20The%20petitioners%20also%20claim%20that%20this%20will%20lead%20to%20the%20creation%20of%20shell%20companies%20and%20rise%20of%20benami%20transactions%20to%20channelise%20undocumented%20money%20into%20the%20political%20and%20electoral%20process%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20October%2010%20during%20the%20preliminary%20hearing%2C%20counsel%20Prashant%20Bhushan%20for%20the%20petitioners%20alleged%20that%20due%20to%20non-decision%20on%20the%20matter%20by%20the%20court%20continuously%20since%202017%2C%20the%20ruling%20party%20has%20been%20enjoying%20the%20fruits%20of%20the%20scheme%20in%20every%20general%20election%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20as%20well%20as%20the%20assembly%20elections%2C%20thus%20upsetting%20the%20level%20playing%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBhushan%20submitted%20that%20the%20scheme%2C%20apart%20from%20having%20been%20fraudulently%20introduced%20through%20a%20money%20bill%2C%20also%20seeks%20to%20legalise%20anonymous%20sources%20of%20political%20funding.%20He%20alleged%20that%20the%20scheme%20violates%20the%20right%20to%20information%20about%20funding%20of%20political%20parties%2C%20and%20promotes%20corruption.%20When%20a%20legislative%20measure%20is%20introduced%20by%20the%20government%20as%20a%20money%20bill%2C%20it%20does%20not%20require%20approval%20from%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBhushan%20explained%20that%20political%20parties%20received%20funds%20most%20likely%20from%20companies%20which%20received%20some%20benefit%20or%20the%20other%20from%20them.%20He%20told%20the%20bench%20that%20as%20corruption-free%20society%20is%20a%20facet%20of%20Article%2021%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20as%20held%20by%20the%20court%2C%20source%20of%20funding%20cannot%20be%20anonymous.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20(SBI)%2C%20as%20the%20designated%20bank%2C%20sells%20these%20bonds%20in%20the%20denominations%20from%20Rs%2010%2C000%20to%20Rs%201%20crore%20to%20anybody%2C%20either%20in%20cash%20or%20through%20bank%20transfers%20(bank%20account%20to%20be%20opened%20if%20there%20is%20a%20cash%20deposit)%2C%20with%20the%20source%20of%20purchase%20kept%20in%20wraps.%20While%20the%20source%20is%20known%20to%20SBI%2C%20it%20is%20obliged%20not%20to%20disclose%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDetails%20regarding%20who%20donates%20to%20which%20political%20party%20and%20what%20amount%20are%20not%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698643495000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F18150906%2FSupreme-Court.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fcitizens-have-no-fundamental-right-to-know-of-source-of-political-funding-ag-to-sc%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22R.%20Venkataramani%20also%20said%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20would%20be%20entering%20the%20domain%20of%20policy%20if%20it%20tried%20to%20regulate%20electoral%20bonds.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fcitizens-have-no-fundamental-right-to-know-of-source-of-political-funding-ag-to-sc%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SC%20rejects%20Sisodia's%20bail%20pleas%20in%20money%20laundering%20cases%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698642858000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104813539%2Cimgsize-19992.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fsupreme-court-rejects-manish-sisodias-bail-pleas-in-money-laundering-cases%2Farticleshow%2F104813552.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Student's%20death%20during%20snatching%3A%20Accused%20killed%20in%20encounter%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698642452000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104815882%2Cimgsize-734943.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fghaziabad%2Fghaziabad-28-year-old-criminal-wanted-in-girls-death-during-phone-snatching-incident-killed-in-encounter%2Farticleshow%2F104812900.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20Friday%2C%20Kirti%20Singh%2C%20a%20B-Tech%20student%20at%20ABES%20College%2C%20was%20injured%20during%20a%20phone-snatching%20incident%20on%20NH-9%20in%20the%20Masuri%20area%20while%20she%20was%20on%20her%20way%20home%20in%20Hapur%20with%20her%20friend%20Diksha%20Jindal%20in%20an%20auto-rickshaw.%20She%20passed%20away%20in%20Yashoda%20Hospital%20in%20Ghaziabad%20on%20Sunday.%20According%20to%20the%20police%2C%20the%20accused%20has%20been%20identified%20as%20Jeetendra%2C%20alias%20Jeetu%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Mishal%20Garhi%20area%20in%20Masuri%2C%20Ghaziabad.%20A%20total%20of%2012%20cases%2C%20including%20robbery%20and%20snatching%2C%20were%20filed%20against%20Jeetendra%20in%20various%20police%20stations%20in%20Delhi-NCR.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22AVISHEK%20KUMAR%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BStrongly%20Oppose%26quot%3B%20India's%20Abstention%20On%20Gaza%20Vote%20At%20UN%20%3A%20Sonia%20Gandhi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20is%20%26quot%3Bstrongly%20opposed%26quot%3B%20to%20India's%20abstention%20on%20the%20recent%20UN%20resolution%20on%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20conflict%2C%20former%20party%20chief%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20said%20on%20Monday%2C%20asserting%20that%20while%20her%20party%20had%20unequivocally%20condemned%20Hamas'%20attacks%2C%20the%20tragedy%20is%20compounded%20by%20the%20Israeli%20state%20now%20focused%20on%20exacting%20revenge%20from%20a%20population%20that%20is%20largely%20as%20helpless%20as%20it%20is%20blameless.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20said%20her%20party's%20longstanding%20position%20has%20been%20to%20support%20direct%20negotiations%20for%20a%20sovereign%20independent%2C%20viable%20and%20secure%20state%20of%20Palestine%20coexisting%20in%20peace%20with%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20article%20in%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fopinion%2Flead%2Fa-war-where-humanity-is-on-trial-now%2Farticle67473719.ece%5C%22%3E%20The%20Hindu%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Mrs%20Gandhi%20said%20%26quot%3Bhumanity%20is%20on%20trial%20now%26quot%3B%2C%20as%20she%20called%20for%20the%20loudest%20and%20most%20powerful%20voices%20to%20be%20for%20a%20cessation%20of%20military%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20collectively%20diminished%20by%20the%20brutal%20attacks%20on%20Israel.%20We%20are%20now%20all%20diminished%20by%20Israel's%20disproportionate%20and%20equally%20brutal%20response.%20How%20many%20more%20lives%20will%20have%20to%20be%20taken%20before%20our%20collective%20conscience%20is%20stirred%20and%20awakened%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20October%207%2C%202023%2C%20on%20the%2050th%20anniversary%20of%20the%20Yom%20Kippur%20War%2C%20Hamas%20launched%20a%20brutal%20attack%20on%20Israel%2C%20killing%20more%20than%20a%20thousand%20people%2C%20mostly%20civilians%2C%20and%20kidnapping%20over%20200%20more%2C%20she%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20unprecedented%20attack%20was%20devastating%20for%20Israel.%20The%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20strongly%20believes%20that%20violence%20has%20no%20place%20in%20a%20decent%20world%2C%20and%20the%20very%20next%20day%20unequivocally%20condemned%20Hamas's%20attacks%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMrs%20Gandhi%20further%20said%20that%20this%20tragedy%20is%2C%20however%2C%20being%20compounded%20by%20the%20Israeli%20military's%20%26quot%3Bindiscriminate%20operations%26quot%3B%20in%20and%20around%20Gaza%20that%20have%20led%20to%20thousands%20of%20deaths%2C%20including%20large%20numbers%20of%20innocent%20children%2C%20women%20and%20men.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20power%20of%20the%20Israeli%20state%20is%20now%20focused%20on%20exacting%20revenge%20from%20a%20population%20that%20is%20largely%20as%20helpless%20as%20it%20is%20blameless.%20The%20destructive%20might%20of%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20potent%20military%20arsenals%20is%20being%20unleashed%20upon%20children%2C%20women%20and%20men%20who%20have%20no%20part%20in%20the%20Hamas%20assault%3B%20they%2C%20instead%2C%20for%20the%20most%20part%2C%20have%20been%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20decades%20of%20discrimination%20and%20suffering%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EArticulating%20the%20Congress's%20stand%20on%20the%20Israel-Palestine%20issue%2C%20she%20said%20there%20can%20be%20no%20peace%20without%20justice.%20%C2%A0Israel's%20unremitting%20blockade%20for%20over%20a%20decade%20and%20a%20half%20has%20reduced%20Gaza%20to%20an%20%26quot%3Bopen-air%20prison%26quot%3B%20for%20its%20two%20million%20inhabitants%20packed%20into%20dense%20cities%20and%20refugee%20camps%2C%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20Jerusalem%20and%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20Israeli%20settlers%20backed%20by%20the%20Israeli%20state%20have%20continued%20to%20push%20out%20Palestinians%20from%20their%20own%20land%20in%20a%20seeming%20effort%20to%20destroy%20the%20vision%20of%20a%20two-state%20solution.%20Peace%20will%20come%20only%20if%20the%20world%2C%20led%20by%20countries%20that%20have%20the%20ability%20to%20influence%20policies%20and%20events%2C%20can%20restart%20the%20process%20of%20restoring%20the%20two-state%20vision%20and%20make%20it%20a%20reality%2C%26quot%3B%20Mrs%20Gandhi%20stressed.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20the%20Congress%20has%20been%20consistent%20over%20the%20years%20in%20its%20strong%20belief%20that%20both%20the%20Palestinians%20and%20Israelis%20have%20the%20right%20to%20live%20in%20a%20just%20peace.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20value%20our%20friendship%20with%20the%20people%20of%20Israel.%20But%20this%20does%20not%20mean%20that%20we%20erase%20from%20our%20memories%2C%20the%20painful%20history%20of%20forced%20dispossession%20of%20the%20Palestinians%20from%20what%20was%20their%20homeland%20for%20centuries%2C%20and%20of%20years%20of%20suppression%20of%20their%20basic%20right%20to%20a%20life%20of%20dignity%20and%20self-respect%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BContrary%20to%20some%20mischievous%20suggestions%2C%20the%20position%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20has%20been%20long-standing%20and%20principled%3A%20it%20is%20to%20support%20direct%20negotiations%20for%20a%20sovereign%20independent%2C%20viable%20and%20secure%20state%20of%20Palestine%20coexisting%20in%20peace%20with%20Israel%2C%26quot%3B%20Mrs%20Gandhi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20pointed%20out%20that%20this%20was%20also%20the%20stand%20taken%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20on%20October%2012%2C%202023.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20noteworthy%20that%20the%20reiteration%20of%20India's%20historic%20position%20on%20Palestine%20came%20only%20after%20Israel%20began%20its%20assault%20on%20Gaza.%20The%20Prime%20Minister%20had%20made%20no%20mention%20of%20Palestinian%20rights%20in%20the%20initial%20statement%20expressing%20complete%20solidarity%20with%20Israel%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20is%20strongly%20opposed%20to%20India's%20abstention%20on%20the%20recent%20United%20Nations%20General%20Assembly%20Resolution%20calling%20for%20an%20'immediate%2C%20durable%20and%20sustained%20humanitarian%20truce%20leading%20to%20a%20cessation%20of%20hostilities'%20between%20Israeli%20forces%20and%20Hamas%20in%20Gaza%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20Congress%20chief%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20unfortunate%20that%20many%20influential%20countries%20are%20being%20wholly%20partisan%20when%20they%20should%20be%20trying%20their%20utmost%20to%20end%20the%20war.%20The%20loudest%20and%20most%20powerful%20voices%20should%20be%20for%20a%20cessation%20of%20military%20activity%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20asserted.%20%C2%A0Otherwise%2C%20this%20cycle%20will%20continue%20and%20make%20it%20difficult%20for%20anyone%20in%20the%20region%20to%20live%20in%20peace%20for%20a%20long%20time%20to%20come%2C%20Mrs%20Gandhi%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20pointed%20out%20that%20in%20this%20war%2C%20as%20it%20is%20now%20described%2C%20entire%20families%20have%20been%20wiped%20out%20and%20neighbourhoods%20have%20been%20reduced%20to%20rubble.%20%C2%A0%26quot%3BThe%20denial%20of%20water%2C%20food%20and%20electricity%20is%20no%20less%20than%20the%20collective%20punishment%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20people.%20The%20outside%20world%2C%20particularly%20those%20who%20want%20to%20help%2C%20is%20largely%20blocked%20out%20of%20Gaza%2C%20with%20relief%20and%20aid%20reaching%20the%20needy%20in%20a%20trickle%2C%20and%20not%20on%20the%20scale%20that%20is%20necessary%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20only%20is%20it%20inhumane%20but%20it%20is%20also%20illegal%20in%20international%20law.%20Very%20few%20Gazans%20are%20untouched%20by%20the%20violence.%20Bottled%20up%20on%20a%20small%2C%20over-densely%20populated%20strip%20of%20territory%2C%20they%20have%20nothing%20to%20fall%20back%20upon.%20And%20now%2C%20even%20the%20occupied%20West%20Bank%20has%20flared%20up%20and%20the%20conflict%20is%20widening%2C%26quot%3B%20Mrs%20Gandhi%20pointed%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENoting%20that%20the%20prospects%20for%20the%20future%20are%20ominous%2C%20Gandhi%20said%20senior%20Israeli%20officials%20have%20spoken%20of%20destroying%20and%20depopulating%20large%20parts%20of%20Gaza.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20Defence%20Minister%20has%20referred%20to%20Palestinians%20as%20%26quot%3Bhuman%20animals%26quot%3B%2C%20she%20said%20and%20added%20that%20this%20%26quot%3Bdehumanising%20language%26quot%3B%20is%20shocking%20coming%20from%20the%20descendants%20of%20those%20who%20themselves%20were%20the%20victims%20of%20the%20Holocaust.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Israeli%20government%20is%20making%20a%20grievous%20error%20in%20equating%20the%20actions%20of%20Hamas%20with%20the%20Palestinian%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20asserted.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20determination%20to%20destroy%20Hamas%2C%20it%20has%20unleashed%20indiscriminate%20death%20and%20destruction%20against%20the%20ordinary%20people%20of%20Gaza%2C%20Mrs%20Gandhi%20said.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20if%20the%20long%20history%20of%20the%20suffering%20of%20the%20Palestinians%20is%20ignored%2C%20by%20what%20logic%20can%20a%20whole%20population%20be%20held%20responsible%20for%20the%20actions%20of%20a%20few%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20the%20article.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20India%20abstaining%20from%20voting%20on%20the%20United%20Nations%20resolution%20on%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20conflict%2C%20opposition%20parties%20on%20Saturday%20had%20asserted%20that%20the%20move%20goes%20against%20everything%20the%20country%20has%20stood%20for%2C%20even%20as%20the%20BJP%20stressed%20that%20India%20will%20never%20be%20on%20the%20side%20of%20terrorism.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOver%201%2C400%20people%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20unprecedented%20attacks%20on%20Israel%20by%20Hamas%20on%20Octobe