0Indian%20cricket%20team%20opener%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Gautam%20Gambhir%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F563-gautam-gambhir-playerprofile%5C%22%3EGautam%20Gambhir%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20played%20a%20great%20impact%20in%20the%20side%20winning%20the%202007%20T20%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20and%20the%202011%20ODI%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%2C%20is%20thoroughly%20impressed%20by%20the%20way%20Rohit%20Sharma%20has%20batted.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLeader%20-%20the%20thing%20he%20wants%20from%20the%20team%2C%20he%20does%20it%20himself.%20If%20you%20expect%20positive%20batting%20from%20your%20teammates%2C%20you%20have%20to%20do%20it%20yourself.%20This%20act%20-%20leading%20from%20the%20front%20-%20you%20have%20to%20do%20it%20yourself.%20No%20kind%20of%20PR%20or%20marketing%20agency%20can%20do%20it%20for%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20said%20on%20Start%20Sports.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20Rohit%20Sharma%20(87)%20top-scored%20for%20India%20against%20England%20in%20Lucknow%20as%20the%20team%20notches%20229%2F9.%20Then%2C%20India%20dismissed%20England%20for%20just%20129.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRohit%20Sharma%20has%20done%20that.%20Maybe%20in%20terms%20of%20run%20tally%2C%20he%20is%20at%20the%20No.%2010%20or%20No.%205%20slot.%20It%20does%20not%20matter.%20But%20your%20aim%20is%20winning%20the%20trophy%20on%20November%2019.%20You%20have%20to%20decide%20whether%20your%20aim%20is%20to%20hit%20a%20100%20or%20win%20the%20World%20Cup.%20If%20your%20aim%20is%20to%20hit%20a%20ton%2C%20then%20you%20play%20that%20way.%20But%20if%20aim%20is%20to%20win%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%20then%20a%20selfless%20captain%20%2C%20like%20the%20way%20Rohit%20Sharma%20has%20batted%2C%20I%20expect%20him%20to%20do%20that%20more.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20in%20a%20match%20against%20England%20at%20the%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%2C%20Rohit%20Sharma%20became%20only%20the%20fifth%20Indian%20batter%20after%20%3