%20any%20information%20on%20the%20event%2C%20it%20is%20anticipated%20to%20be%20a%20major%20Mac%20product%20launch%2C%20potentially%20showcasing%20new%20MacBooks%20and%20iMacs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20To%20Expect%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftechcrunch.com%2F2023%2F10%2F27%2Fapples-scary-fast-mac-event-how-to-watch-and-what-to-expect%2F%5C%22%3ETechCrunch%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20'Scary%20Fast'%20is%20probably%20a%20reference%20to%20new%20chips%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20apparent%20Halloween%20undertones.%20Looking%20at%20the%20event's%20invite%2C%20it%20is%20most%20likely%20that%20the%20tech%20giant%20will%20make%20an%20announcement%20on%20new%20Macs%20because%20of%20the%20silver%20Apple%20logo%20and%20the%20augmented%20reality%20effect%20that%20turns%20it%20into%20a%20Finder%20widget.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EApple%20has%20not%20updated%20its%2024-inch%20iMac%20since%202021.%20As%20per%20an%20old%20report%20based%20on%20Bloomberg's%20Mark%20Gurman%20newsletter%2C%20it%20was%20noted%20that%20Apple%20will%20introduce%20a%20refreshed%2024-inch%20iMac%20at%20the%20next%20event.%20Additionally%2C%20he%20mentioned%20that%20the%20larger%20iMac%20Pro%20model%20will%20be%20available%20in%20late%202024%20or%20early%202025.%20However%2C%20according%20to%20industry%20expert%20Ming-Chi%20Kuo%2C%20the%20new%2024-inch%20iMac%20will%20be%20released%20in%20the%20coming%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EApple%20will%20also%20likely%20unveil%20its%20next-generation%20silicon%20chip%2C%20M3.%20It%20is%20anticipated%20that%20the%20company%20will%20showcase%20new%20iMac%20machines%20that%20include%20the%20new%20processor%2C%20a%20move%20that%20could%20help%20increase%20Mac%20sales.%20It%20is%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20sales%20have%20decreased%20this%20year%20because%20of%20lower%20demand%2C%20surplus%20inventory%2C%20and%20a%20deteriorating%20macroeconomic%20environment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20Apple%20introduced%20MacBook%20Pros%20with%20M2%20Pro%20and%20M2%20Max%20chips%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20a%20Mac%20mini.%20Later%2C%20they%20also%20released%20Apple's%20first%2015-inch%20MacBook%20Air%20and%20Mac%20Studio%20models%2C%20and%20Mac%20Pro%2C%20which%20is%20the%20first%20device%20to%20employ%20Apple%20Silicon%2C%20the%20company's%20in-house%20chips.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20also%20possible%20that%20'Scary%20Fast'%20will%20witness%20the%20launch%20of%20new%20accessories%20as%20the%20tech%20giant%20moves%20to%20a%20USB-C%20universal%20charging%20system%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20And%20Where%20To%20Watch%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20event%2C%20scheduled%20for%20October%2030%20at%205%20pm%20Pacific%20Time%20(5%3A30%20am%20on%20October%2031%20IST)%2C%20will%20be%20live-streamed%20on%20Apple's%20official%20website.%20Although%20the%20streaming%20time%20is%20also%20something%20unusual%20for%20the%20company%2C%20it%20is%20likely%20meant%20to%20fit%20the%20spooky%20Halloween%20theme.%20The%20company%20sent%20out%20invites%20for%20the%20event%20last%20week%2C%20however%2C%20the%20event%20will%20only%20be%20online%20as%20there%20is%20no%20in-person%20attendance%20allowed.%20%C2%A0The%20live%20stream%20will%20also%20be%20available%20on%20Apple's%20official%20YouTube%20channel%20and%20the%20Apple%20TV%20app.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ELast%20Event%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3EApple%20held%20its%20Wonderlust%20event%20on%20September%2012%20and%20launched%20the%20company's%20top-of-the-line%20iPhone%2015%20series%20and%20Apple%20Watch%20Series%209.%20The%20company%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fapple-bows-to-eu-and-unveils-iphone-with-usb-c-charger-kaiann-drance-4384453%5C%22%3Eintroduced%20the%20USB-C%20charging%20port%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20bidding%20farewell%20to%20Apple's%20traditional%20Lightning%20cable.%20The%20iPhone%2015%20with%20128GB%20of%20base%20storage%20starts%20at%20Rs