the%20perfect%20time%20for%20them%20to%20take%20on%20the%20project%20because%20of%20their%20work%20schedule.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20composite%20image%20of%20the%20couple%20during%20the%20restoration%20process%20of%20the%20abandoned%20Japanese%20home.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652f7a2f211def8ed837ceae%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20couple%20did%20almost%20all%20the%20work%20themselves%2C%20with%20help%20from%20their%20son.%3Cp%3EGilles%20Beaufils%2FBase%20Camp%20Imari%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20they%20weren't%20busy%20with%20work%2C%20the%20trio%20could%20mostly%20focus%20on%20renovating%20the%20place.%20It%20would%20have%20been%20difficult%20to%20get%20anything%20done%20otherwise%2C%20Beaufils%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20renovated%20most%20of%20the%20property%20themselves%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20did%20all%20that%20we%20could%20do%20and%20then%20we%20left%20the%20electricity%20and%20plumbing%20jobs%20to%20the%20professionals%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20renovation%20process%20was%20fun%2C%20Beaufils%20said%20he%20would%20never%C2%A0do%20this%20again%20because%20it%20was%20physically%20and%20mentally%20arduous.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222453%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Progress%20photo%20of%20the%20restoration%20process.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652f87a6211def8ed837d04c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221840%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EProgress%20photo%20of%20the%20restoration%20process.%3Cp%3EGilles%20Beaufils%2FBase%20Camp%20Imari%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20worked%20six%20days%20a%20week%20for%20four%20months%20with%20no%20breaks%20and%20sometimes%20even%20had%20to%20squeeze%20in%20trips%20back%20to%20Tokyo%20to%20attend%20to%20work%20matters%2C%