3EThe%20place%20became%20much%20more%20popular%20with%20tourists%20than%20Beaufils%20initially%20expected%2C%20but%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20slowed%20everything%20down.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20three%20years%2C%20business%20became%20very%20slow%2C%20but%20we%20were%20working%20on%20our%20other%20businesses%20while%20staying%20in%20the%20countryside%2C%20which%20was%20good%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20would%20have%20been%20in%20Tokyo%20otherwise.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221132%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20cozy%20corner%20in%20the%20cafe.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652f7e10211def8ed837cf04%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22848%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20cozy%20corner%20in%20the%20cafe.%3Cp%3EGilles%20Beaufils%2FBase%20Camp%20Imari%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20pandemic%20restrictions%20started%20to%20ease%2C%20travelers%20started%20coming%20back%20to%20Japan%20in%20troves%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20that%20time%2C%20the%20couple%20decided%20to%20move%20out%20of%20the%20lodge%20and%20to%20the%20town%20of%20Itoshima%20in%20Fukuoka%2C%20which%20is%20a%2040-minute%20drive%20away.%20Fukuoka%20is%20about%20an%20hour%20and%2045%20minutes%20from%20Tokyo%20by%20plane.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeaufils%20and%20his%20wife%20now%20split%20their%20time%20between%20their%20home%20and%20the%20lodge.%20They're%20usually%20at%20the%20lodge%20over%20the%20weekends%20or%20whenever%20there's%20a%20booking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20one%20full-time%20staff%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20caf%C3%A9%2C%20and%20then%20we%20have%20two%20to%20three%20people%20who%20come%20to%20help.%20And%20then%20we%20have%20me%20and%20my%20wife%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20things%2C%20including%20the%20lodge%2C%20the%20paperwork%2C%20the%20gardening%2C%26quot%3B%20Beaufils%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22983%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20ca