0interested%20in%20buying%20akiyas%20should%20have%20an%20idea%20of%20how%20they%20intend%20to%20restore%20the%20property%20before%20biting%20the%20bullet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAre%20you%20going%20to%20make%20the%20reform%20yourself%20or%20you%20are%20going%20to%20ask%20somebody%20to%20do%20that%3F%26quot%3B%20Beaufils%20said.%20%26quot%3BEspecially%20if%20you%20are%20overseas%20because%20you%20need%20to%20have%20a%20visa%20or%20you%20can%20only%20come%20three%20months%20at%20a%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20those%20living%20in%20Japan%20but%C2%A0working%20full-time%20might%20end%20up%20outsourcing%20the%20project%20to%20external%20contractors%20due%20to%20their%20schedules%2C%20which%20can%20cause%20costs%20to%20balloon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20opportunities%20to%20live%20in%20the%20beautiful%20countryside%20with%20a%20nice%20cheap%20house.%20But%20you%20have%20to%20be%20careful%20also%20because%20sometimes%2C%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20it's%20not%20so%20cheap%20anymore%2C%26quot%3B%20Beaufils%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20you%20recently%20bought%20or%20renovated%20your%20dream%20home%20and%20want%20to%20share%20the%20details%20and%20photos%20of%20the%20process%3F%20Email%20this%20reporter%2C%20Amanda%20Goh%2C%20at%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%2280f64ddfef21e4a8e194a42d83dd5953%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%22100%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aagoh%40insider.com%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eagoh%40insider.com%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcouple-ditches-city-life-restore-abandoned-home-diy-akiya-japan-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698631758000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653b6ad10487ff031cb01909%3Fformat%3Djpe