ers%2C%20showed%20that%20knowledge%20of%20machine%20learning%2C%20open-source%20AI%20software%2C%20and%20deep%20learning%20salaries%20were%20the%20skills%20employers%20valued%20the%20most.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20findings%20have%20profound%20implications%20for%20individuals%2C%20businesses%2C%20and%20policymakers%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dr%20Fabian%20Stephany%2C%20one%20of%20the%20study's%20authors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20recognizing%20the%20value%20of%20complementary%20skills%2C%20we%20can%20better%20guide%20workers%20on%20their%20individual%20reskilling%20journeys%20in%20times%20of%20technological%20change.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS0048733323001828%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWhat%20is%20the%20Price%20of%20a%20Skill%3F%20The%20Value%20of%20Complementarity%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3B%20was%20published%20in%20the%20academic%20%3C%2Fspan%3Ejournal%20%26quot%3BResearch%20Policy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20findings%20come%20as%20employers%20and%20workers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcareer-growth-most-important-soft-skills-ai-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Egrapple%20with%20the%20impact%20of%20generative%20AI%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20following%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-may-be-fastest-growing-app-in-history-ubs-study-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Elaunch%20of%20ChatGPT%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20Google%20Cloud%20Next%20conference%20in%20London%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20Unilever%20chief%20technology%20officer%20Adam%20Raeburn-Jones%20said%20AI%20skills%20will%20be%20a%20crucial%20factor%20in%20future%20hiring%20decisions.%20Jobseekers%20who%20know%20their%20way%20around%20the%20new%20technology%20would%20have%20a%20natural%20advantage%2C%20he%20believed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20people%20who%20do%20really%20well%20will%20be%20the%20ones%20who%20learn%20how%20to%20harness%20the%20technology%20the%20best%2C%26quot%3B%20Raeburn-Jones%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20next%20generation%20will%20probably%20pick%20that%20up%20quicker%20than%20those%20of%20us%20already%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStephan%20Pretorius%2C%20CTO%20of%20advertising%20agency%20WPP%2C%20said%20his%20company%20was%20now%20hiring%20people%20with%20specialist%20AI%20skills%2C%20and%20that%20employers%20would%20have%20to%20battle%20to%20attract%20young%20workers%20with%20AI%20expertise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20skills%20that%20they%20are%20coming%20into%20the%20job%20market%20with%20now%20are%20fundamentally%20different%20than%20ten%20years%20ago%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20think%20the%20learning%20paths%20are%20going%20to%20be%20the%20same%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20people%20entering%20the%20industry%20are%20coming%20into%20the%20workplace%20at%20ease%20with%20really%20sophisticated%20technology.%20Young%20people%20are%20not%20naive%2C%20they%20understand%20that%20this%20is%20a%20fundamental%20shift%20in%20how%20we%20work%2C%20and%20they%20will%20start%20to%20go%20for%20companies%20that%20will%20help%20them%20access%20these%20tools.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOded%20Netzer%2C%20a%20business%20professor%20at%20Columbia%20University%2C%20told%20Insider%20that%20prioritization%20of%20workers%20who%20can%20use%20AI%20was%20already%20happening%20in%20sectors%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fpluralsight-research-finds-74-of-software-developers-are-planning-to-upskill-in-ai-assisted-coding-1032716932%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ecoding%20and%20programming%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20would%20only%20become%20more%20common.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20who%20learn%20how%20to%20use%20AI%20quickly%20will%20be%20in%20high%20demand%2C%26quot