%20contexts%20within%20this%20hypocrisy.%20Firstly%2C%20why%20is%20Sunak%E2%80%99s%20speech%20from%20King%20David%20Hotel%20important%3F%20Secondly%2C%20why%20has%20the%20world%20forgotten%20Irgun%20%E2%80%93%20the%20militant%20Israeli%20Zionist%20terror%20group%3F%20Lastly%2C%20what%20are%20Sunak%E2%80%99s%20ties%20with%20Israel%2C%20and%20what%20compels%20him%20to%20speak%20against%20the%20Boycott%2C%20Divestment%20and%20Sanctions%20(BDS)%20movement%20against%20Israel%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELet%20us%20go%20back%20in%20history%20a%20bit.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20July%2022%2C%201946%2C%20the%20same%20King%20David%20Hotel%2C%20which%20was%20then%20the%20British%20Headquarters%20of%20%E2%80%98Mandate%20Palestine%E2%80%99%20as%20well%20as%20British%20Criminal%20Investigation%20Division%20(CID)%2C%20was%20attacked%20by%20Irgun%20forces%20%E2%80%93%20an%20Israeli%20Zionist%20paramilitary%20organisation.%20The%20attack%20at%20King%20David%20Hotel%20led%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jewishvirtuallibrary.org%2Fbombing-of-the-king-david-hotel%5C%22%3Ehigh%20casualty%20toll%3A%20a%20total%20of%2091%20killed%20and%2045%20injured.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20addressing%20the%20House%20of%20Commons%2C%20then%20British%20Prime%20Minister%20Clement%20Attlee%20called%20it%20%E2%80%98an%20insane%20act%20of%20terrorism%E2%80%99.%20Daniel%20Lipson%2C%20who%20was%20the%20Jewish%20member%20of%20the%20opposition%20Conservative%20party%2C%20also%20declared%20that%20Irgun%E2%80%99s%20bomb%20attack%20on%20King%20David%20Hotel%20was%20%E2%80%9Ca%20dishonour%20and%20shame%20to%20the%20name%20of%20Jew%E2%80%9D.%20The%20Earl%20of%20Winterton%20described%20Irgun%20as%20%E2%80%9Cvile%20and%20treacherous%20as%20foe%20as%20Nazis%E2%80%9D.%20Einstein%2C%20who%20refused%20to%20be%20the%20president%20of%20Israel%2C%20had%20called%20Irgun%20%E2%80%9CNazi%20and%20Fascist%20parties%E2%80%9D%20and%20described%20it%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cterrorist%2C%20right%20wing%2C%20chauvinist%20organization%E2%80%9D%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%201948.%20Other%20significant%20Jewish%20figures%20like%20Hannah%20Arendt%2C%20Jessurun%20Cardozo%20and%20Sidney%20Hook%20had%20called%20Irgun%20as%20%E2%80%9Ca%20terrorist%2C%C2%A0right-wing%2C%C2%A0chauvinist%C2%A0organisation%20in%20Palestine%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20why%20was%20King%20David%20Hotel%20so%20important%2C%20one%20might%20ask%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBuilt%20in%201929%2C%20King%20David%20Hotel%20was%20meant%20to%20be%20a%20luxurious%20escapade%20in%20the%20pyretic%20Palestinian%20environment%2C%20with%20Swiss%20interior%20designing%2C%20%3Cem%3ELa%20regence%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%93%20the%20basement%20nightclub%20and%20Grand%20Lobby%20for%20tea%20for%20visiting%20dignitaries%2C%20potentates%20and%20well-heeled.%20No%20doubt%2C%20it%20attracted%20a%20lot%20of%20politicians%2C%20diplomats%2C%20journalist%20and%20even%20spies.%20Even%20though%20the%20hotel%20was%20surrounded%20by%20armored%20cars%2C%20roadblocks%2C%20checkpoints%20and%20barbed%20wires%20and%20machine%20gun-pit%2C%20it%20remained%20open%20to%20the%20public.%20In%20the%20words%20of%20American%20historian%20Thurston%20Clarke%20(author%20of%20%3Cem%3EBy%20Blood%20and%20Fire%3A%20Attack%20on%20the%20King%20David%20Hotel%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20King%20David%20was%20built%20and%20operated%20in%20a%20time-honoured%20Middle%20Eastern%20fashion.%20Azra%20Mosseri%2C%20a%20Jewish-Egyptian%20banker%2C%20had%20purchased%20a%20four-and-a-half-acre%20lot%20in%20Jerusalem%20from%20a%20Greek%20Orthodox%20monastery.%20To%20finance%20construction%2C%20he%20sold%20shares%20in%20Palestine%20Hotels%20Ltd.%20to%20American%20and%20Egyptian%20Jews%2C%20and%20to%20Swiss%20investors%2C%20retaining%20for%20his%20family%20a%20controlling%20interest.%20A%20Swiss%20architect%20designed%20the%20hotel%2C%20a%20Jewish%20architect%20supervised%20its%20construction%2C%20and%20Arab%20workmen%20built%20it.%20The%20company%20hired%20Swiss%20and%20Jews%20to%20manage%20it%2C%20French%20and%20Italians%20to%20cook%2C%20and%20local%20Arabs%20and%20Africans%20from%20the%20Sudan%20to%20wait%20on%20tables%2C%20clean%20rooms%2C%20mop%20floors%20and%20wash%20dishes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMenachem%20Begin%2C%20the%20sixth%20prime%20minister%20of%20Israel%20%E2%80%93%20also%20a%20profound%20ideological%20mentor%20of%20current%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20%E2%80%93%20was%20the%20leader%20of%20Irgun.%20Begin%20was%20described%20by%20the%20British%20government%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Cleader%20of%20the%20notorious%C2%A0terrorist%C2%A0organisation%E2%80%9D.%20In%201946%2C%20a%20month%20before%20the%20bombing%2C%20the%20British%20Military%20Organisation%20had%20seized%20highly%20sensitive%20documents%20which%20could%20implicate%20Haganah%20(a%20Zionist%20military%20organisation%20representing%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20Jews%20in%20Palestine%20from%201920%20to%201948).%20Therefore%2C%20Begin%20believed%20that%20these%20intelligence%20files%20were%20located%20in%20King%20David%20Hotel%20and%20%E2%80%98hoped%20that%20the%20Irgun%E2%80%99s%20bombs%20would%20destroy%20the%20incriminating%20material%E2%80%99.%20Later%2C%20to%20the%20surprise%20of%20Begin%2C%20Haganah%20backtracked%20and%20broadcast%20a%20statement%20over%20its%20clandestine%20radio%20station%20%3Cem%3EKol%20Israel%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20July%2023.%20It%20denounced%20the%20%E2%80%9Cheavy%20loss%20of%20life%20caused%20by%20the%20dissidents%E2%80%99%20operation%20at%20the%20King%20David%20Hotel%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20in%20his%20memoir%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Revolt%3A%20Story%20of%20The%20Irgun%3C%2Fem%3E%20(1951)%2C%20Begin%20asked%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20was%20the%20King%20David%20Hotel%20not%20evacuated%3F%E2%80%9D%20He%20claimed%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthere%20are%20certain%20facts%20which%20are%20beyond%20all%20doubt%E2%80%9D%3A%20first%2C%20that%20the%20Irgun%E2%80%99s%20warnings%20were%20inexplicably%20ignored%3B%20and%2C%20second%2C%20that%20the%20hotel%E2%80%99s%20evacuation%20was%20specifically%20prevented.%20%E2%80%9C%5BT%5Dhere%20is%20reason%20to%20believe%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Irgun%20leader%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthat%20a%20specific%20order%20was%20given%2C%20by%20someone%20in%20authority%2C%20that%20the%20warning%20to%20leave%20the%20hotel%20should%20be%20ignored.%20Why%20was%20this%20stupid%20order%20given%3F%20Who%20was%20responsible%20for%20it%3F%E2%80%9D%20Although%20Begin%20provides%20no%20answers%2C%20his%20version%20of%20events%20%E2%80%93%20as%20the%20controversy%20over%20the%20wording%20of%20the%20anniversary%20plaque%20evidences%20%E2%80%93%20has%20assumed%20almost%20totemic%20importance%20in%20the%20mythology%20of%20both%20the%20Irgun%E2%80%99s%20struggle%20and%20the%20history%20of%20pre-state%20Israel%2C%20as%20stated%20by%20Professor%20Bruce%20Hoffman%2C%20Georgetown%20University%2C%20Washington%2C%20D.C.%20Nevertheless%2C%20Irgun%20members%20were%20later%20absorbed%20in%20the%20Israeli%20Defence%20Forces.%20It%20was%20the%20predecessor%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%C2%A0right-wing%C2%A0Herut%C2%A0(or%20%E2%80%9CFreedom%E2%80%9D)%20party%2C%20which%20is%20today%20known%20as%20Likud%20Party%2C%20as%20stated%20by%20Israeli%20sociologist%20Shmuel%20Noah%20Eisenstadt.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20irony%20of%20this%20decades-old%20conspiracy%20does%20not%20lose%20its%20merit%20when%20current%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20had%20openly%20stated%2C%20%E2%80%9CImagine%20that%20Hamas%20or%20Hezbollah%20would%20call%20the%20military%20headquarters%20in%20Tel%20Aviv%20and%20say%2C%20%E2%80%98We%20have%20placed%20a%20bomb%20and%20we%20are%20asking%20you%20to%20evacuate%20the%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20in%202006%2C%20as%20quoted%20by%20Parker%20and%20Farrell%20in%20%E2%80%9CBritish%20anger%20at%20terror%20celebration.%E2%80%9D%20The%20same%20nonchalance%20of%202006%20was%20followed%20by%20the%20Israeli%20military%20in%20October%202023%2C%20when%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timesofisrael.com%2Fliveblog_entry%2Fegyptian-intelligence-official-says-israel-ignored-repeated-warnings-of-something-big%2F%5C%22%3EEgyptian%20intelligence%20officer%3C%2Fa%3E%20stated%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20warned%20them%20an%20explosion%20of%20the%20situation%20is%20coming%2C%20and%20very%20soon%2C%20and%20it%20would%20be%20big.%20But%20they%20underestimated%20such%20warnings.%E2%80%9D%20Later%2C%20Michael%20McCaul%2C%20the%20chair%20of%20the%20US%20House%20foreign%20affairs%20committee%2C%20spoke%20after%20an%20intelligence%20briefing%20to%20senior%20members%20of%20Congress%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2Foct%2F12%2Fisrael-hamas-war-egypt-warned-foreign-affairs-gaza%5C%22%3Esaid%20it%20was%20not%20clear%20at%20what%20level%20the%20warning%20was%20given.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReturning%20to%20Rishi%20Sunak%E2%80%99s%20visit%20to%20Israel%20and%20stay%20at%20King%20David%20Hotel%2C%20the%20hypocrisy%20now%20unfolds.%20Sunak%20spoke%20from%20the%20same%20hotel%20this%20time%2C%20but%20against%20Palestinian%20terror.%20Any%20mention%20of%20Irgun%E2%80%99s%20terrorism%20has%20been%20replaced%20with%20%E2%80%98jihadist%E2%80%99%20terrorism%20and%20Islamophobia.%20Why%20did%20Sunak%20forget%20what%20Zionist%20terrorism%20had%20done%20to%20the%20British%20in%20Palestine%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20his%20international%20reputation%20in%20tatters%2C%20Sunak%20continues%20to%20employ%20the%20same%20hyperbole%20of%20British%20hypocrisy.%20He%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FRishiSunak%2Fstatus%2F1714895569334735124%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Etweeted%3C%2Fa%3E%20his%20support%20for%20Israel%2C%20stating%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FRishiSunak%2Fstatus%2F1714925911290663286%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3ETo%20have%20a%20child%20taken%20from%20you%20is%20a%20parent%E2%80%99s%20worst%20nightmare%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%99%20He%20remains%20mum%20on%20the%20child%20death%20toll%20in%20Gaza%20that%20has%20reached%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.savethechildren.net%2Fnews%2Fleast-2000-children-killed-gaza-airstrikes-continue-unabated%5C%22%3E2%2C000.%20%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0Photo-ops%20and%20hand-shaking%20with%20Crown%20Prince%20of%20Saudi%20Arabia%20Mohammad%20Bin%20Salman%2C%20Egyptian%20President%20Sisi%20and%20Palestinian%20President%20Abbas%20were%20meant%20for%20the%20optics%20of%20a%20symbolic%20visit.%20On%20October%2023%2C%20he%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2F10DowningStreet%2Fstatus%2F1716498165778600024%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%20stated%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%98On%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20deep%20knowledge%20of%20our%20intelligence%20and%20weapons%20experts%2C%20the%20British%20government%20judges%20that%20the%20explosion%20at%20the%20al-Ahli%20Arab%20hospital%20was%20likely%20caused%20by%20a%20missile%20%E2%80%93%20or%20part%20of%20one%20%E2%80%93%20that%20was%20launched%20from%20within%20Gaza%20towards%20Israel.%E2%80%99%20As%20usual%2C%20the%20deep%20knowledge%20of%20intelligence%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20shared.%20But%20in%20reality%2C%20why%20did%20Sunak%20not%20call%20for%20a%20ceasefire%20but%20instead%20of%20%E2%80%98specific%20pauses%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20conflict%3F%20%E2%80%9CHow%20much%20worse%20does%20the%20situation%20%5Bin%20Gaza%5D%20need%20to%20get%20before%20he%20will%20join%20us%20in%20calls%20for%20a%20humanitarian%20ceasefire%3F%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FBBCPolitics%2Fstatus%2F1717143425223360917%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3ESNP%20MP%20Mhairi%20Black%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20asked%20the%20PM.%20%E2%80%9CI%20cannot%20understand%20the%20PM%E2%80%99s%20position%2C%20or%20Keir%20Starmer%E2%80%99s%20unwillingness%20to%20call%20on%20all%20parties%20to%20commit%20to%20an%20immediate%20ceasefire.%20How%20many%20more%20children%20have%20to%20die%3F%E2%80%9D%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fuk%2Fhumza-yousaf-rishi-sunak-gaza-prime-minister-first-minister-b2435773.html%5C%2