n%20the%20last%20day%20of%20the%20camp%2C%20an%20exhibition%20would%20be%20organised%20for%20the%20parents%20where%20they%20could%20see%20what%20their%20children%20had%20been%20doing%20during%20the%20camp.%20A%20two-hour%20performance%20by%20the%20students%20would%20be%20followed%20with%20tea%20and%20snacks%20for%20everyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20how%20did%20an%20MS%20patient%20manage%20to%20do%20all%20this%3F%20Ask%20her%20and%20Sudha%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CAll%20you%20need%20is%20courage%20and%20support%20from%20the%20family.%E2%80%9D%20She%20is%20immensely%20grateful%20to%20her%20husband%20who%20took%20such%20good%20care%20of%20her%20down%20the%20years%2C%20without%20a%20single%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESudha%20lost%20her%20husband%20to%20cancer%20a%20decade%20ago.%C2%A0%20The%20couple%20has%20no%20children.%20%E2%80%9CDespite%20all%20that%20she%20has%20gone%20through%2C%20she%20has%20a%20ready%20smile%20for%20everyone%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jayashree.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMamtha%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CShe%20taught%20us%20to%20delegate%20work%20and%20encouraged%20us%20to%20think%20of%20it%20as%20%E2%80%98our%20camp%E2%80%99.%20We%20all%20learnt%20a%20lot%20from%20this%20endeavour%20of%20hers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20after%20almost%20three%20decades%2C%20some%20of%20the%20students%20share%20their%20fond%20memories%20of%20the%20summer%20camps.%20Manasa%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CAlways%20calm%20and%20composed%20with%20a%20smiling%20face%2C%20Sudha%20ma%E2%80%99am%20was%20the%20calm%20within%20the%20storm%20of%20kids%20at%20Siddhi%20Creations.%20She%20embodies%20Maria%20Montessori%E2%80%99s%20(an%20Italian%20educator)%20words%2C%20%E2%80%98follow%20the%20child%E2%80%99.%20She%20gave%20us%20the%20freedom%20to%20create%20and%20thrive.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERajath%2C%20who%20is%20an%20advocate%20today%2C%20notes%20how%20%E2%80%9CSudha%20aunty%20showered%20the%20same%20love%20on%20all%20of%20us%20and%20took%20care%20of%20all%20details%2C%20giving%20us%20the%20lesson%20of%20what%20true%20leadership%20was.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20Vijetha%2C%20who%20works%20as%20an%20HR%20in%20an%20MNC%2C%20Siddhi%20Creations%20and%20the%20camps%20were%20%E2%80%9Can%20important%20part%20of%20my%20childhood%2C%20in%20framing%20our%20minds%20and%20adding%20value.%E2%80%9D%20Harshith%2C%20another%20student%20of%20the%20camp%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20green%20surroundings%2C%20the%20teachers%20and%20Sudha%20ma%E2%80%99am%20with%20a%20happy%20face%20are%20unforgettable.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESudha%20echoes%20these%20feelings%20when%20she%20says%20that%20it%20was%20the%20children%E2%80%99s%20smile%20and%20happiness%20that%20was%20the%20best%20part%20of%20the%20summer%20camps.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20a%20sense%20of%20satisfaction%20and%20contentment%20in%20running%20the%20camps%2C%E2%80%9D%20smiles%20the%20octogenarian%20from%20her%20wheelchair.%C2%A0%20Her%20voice%20is%20now%20feeble%20but%20the%20spirit%20is%20as%20strong%20as%20ever.%20There%20is%20talk%20of%20reviving%20the%20camps%20among%20the%20teachers%20who%20are%20excited%20and%20ready.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAuthored%20by%20Jayalakshmi%20Menon.%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EAll%20picture%20credits%20go%20to%20Sudha%20Iyengar.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698072965000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FIMG-20230928-WA0004_11zon-1698072330.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D332837%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20brainchild%20of%20Sudha%20Iyengar%2C%20Siddhi%20Creations%20was%20a%20venture%20to%20keep%20young%20children%20engaged%20fruitfully%20and%20joyfully%20during%20summer%20vacations%20while%20also%20picking%20up%20on%20essential%20life%20skills.%20With%20managing%20her%20Multiple%20Sclerosis%20condition%2C%20Sudha's%20smile%20for%20everyone%20who%20enters%20her%20