n%20that%20comes%20from%20making%20people%20laugh.%20So%20many%20come%20up%20to%20me%20and%20share%20the%20changes%20in%20their%20lives%20after%20following%20my%20tips.%20They%20have%20tears%20in%20their%20eyes%20as%20they%20share%20their%20stories.%20It%20just%20leaves%20me%20awestruck.%20I%20just%20want%20people%20to%20get%20healthier%20and%20receive%20fewer%20patients%20at%20the%20hospital%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20his%20work%20in%20weight%20loss%2C%20a%20particular%20incident%20deeply%20touched%20the%20gastroenterologist.%20In%20one%20of%20his%20initial%20videos%2C%20he%20addressed%20the%20safety%20of%20COVID-19%20vaccines%2C%20prompting%20an%20elderly%20woman%20from%20Madurai%20to%20receive%20the%20vaccine.%20%E2%80%9CI%20received%20a%20letter%20from%20a%20woman%20in%20Thootukudi.%20She%20had%20lost%20her%20father%20to%20COVID%20as%20the%20vaccine%20was%20not%20available%20then.%20She%20said%20that%20her%20mother%20took%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F326043%2Ftwo-moms-serve-the-magic-of-home-cooked-eco-friendly-dabbas-to-thousands-in-london%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evaccine%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20seeing%20my%20video.%20She%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98At%20least%2C%20I%20have%20my%20mother%20today%2C%20thanks%20to%20you%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Pal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20I%20can%20change%20somebody%E2%80%99s%20life%20sitting%20in%20Sacramento%2C%20talking%20to%20a%20camera%2C%20why%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20I%20do%20it%3F%20It%20is%20truly%20satisfying%20as%20well%20as%20fun%20for%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDr%20Pal%20contributes%20his%20social%20media%20earnings%20to%20the%20Aishwaryam%20Trust.%20You%20can%20contribute%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faishwaryamtrust.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C